hat%20we%20refrain%20from%20giving%20any%20further%20comment%20about%20this%20incident.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20trial%20was%20scheduled%20to%20break%20for%20the%20holidays%20on%20Friday%20afternoon%2C%20anyway.%20Meanwhile%2C%20jurors%20have%20been%20told%20to%20completely%20avoid%20social%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20it%20may%20seem%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20it's%20that%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3EGlanville%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20mandate%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20in%20place%20through%20the%20trial%20after%20a%20juror%20told%20the%20judge%20she'd%20found%20a%20video%20of%20pre-trial%20proceedings%20online.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20dust%20up%20followed%20another%20public%20airing%20of%20the%20conditions%20the%20jury%20is%20facing%20that%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Glanville's%20answer%20to%20a%20juror's%20gutsy%20request%20for%20an%20occasional%20free%20lunch.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20man%20said%20his%20request%20%26quot%3Bfeels%20like%20a%20long%20shot%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20can%20we%20get%2C%20like%2C%20lunch%20maybe%20every%20two%20weeks%20or%20so%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGlanville%20feigned%20indignation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYou%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20nerve%2C%20man.%20You%20trying%20to%20ask%20me%20for%20lunch%3F%26quot%3B%20Glanville%20said%2C%20before%20explaining%20Fulton%20County%20has%20%26quot%3Bbad%20credit%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20no%20longer%20has%20money%20to%20provide%20amenities%20for%20jurors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20one%20of%20those%20things%20I%20wish%20I%20could%20provide%20you%20at%20this%20point%20in%20time%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20in%20the%20position%20to%20do%20so.%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20that%20once%20you%20become%20a%20deliberating%20jury%2C%20I%20can%20make%20some%20arrangements%20for%20some%20substance%2C%26quot%3B%20Glanville%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20that%20point%2C%20the%20trial%20was%20down%20to%2015%20jurors%20%E2%80%94%20only%2012%20will%20deliberate%20%E2%80%94%20after%20Judge%20Granville%20dismissed%20a%20woman%20who%20said%20she%20needed%20to%20attend%20a%20medical%20appointment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20took%2010%20months%20for%20Granville%20and%20the%20attorneys%20to%20select%20the%20jurors%20because%20of%20the%20unusual%20scope%20of%20the%20case%20and%20the%20expected%20length%20of%20the%20trial.%20The%20selection%20process%20was%20rife%20with%20its%20own%20viral%20moments%2C%20including%20a%20courtroom%20drug%20deal%20caught%20on%20camera%20and%20a%20prospective%20juror%20ordered%20to%20write%20a%2030-page%20essay%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20jury%20service%20after%20she%20skipped%20a%20selection%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20didn't%20take%20long%20for%20some%20of%20the%20jurors%20themselves%20to%20go%20viral.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Nov.%2029%2C%20the%20third%20day%20of%20trial%2C%20Glanville%20called%20the%20attorneys%20into%20his%20chambers%20after%20screenshots%20from%20the%20trial%20live%20stream%20surfaced%20online%20showing%20the%20faces%20of%20four%20jurors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESites%20such%20as%20the%20hip-hop%20gossip%20powerhouse%20No%20Jumper%20posted%20a%20screenshot%20as%20well%20as%20a%20clip%20of%20the%20camera%20inadvertently%20panning%20to%20them.%20%26quot%3BFans%20on%20Social%20Media%20Are%20Already%20Identifying%20Jury%20Members%20in%20Young%20Thug's%20Trial%20After%20Cameras%20Accidentally%20Revealed%20Their%20Faces.%26quot%3B%20Glanville%20cited%20the%20filming%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bsecurity%20issue%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20was%20%26quot%3Bunrelated%26quot%3B%20when%20he%20asked%20the%20cameraman%20not%20to%20continue%20filming%20the%20witness%2C%20an%20Atlanta%20police%20detective%20who'd%20already%20testified%20on%20camera%20for%20several%20hours.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20prosecutors%20said%20they'd%20realized%20the%20photos%20of%20the%20jurors%20were%20more%20widespread%20than%20they%20first%20thought%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20intervene%2C%20but%20the%20judge%20said%20he%20wasn't%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20to%20weird%20them%20out%26quot%3B%20by%20telling%20them%20a%20few%20had%20been%20caught%20on%20camera.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20another%20juror%20told%20the%20judge%20she%20was%20concerned%20the%20jury%20could%20be%20seen%20on%20a%20courtroom%20camera%20stream%20after%20she%20saw%20a%20months-old%20video%20from%20pre-trial%20proceedings%20online.%20She%20said%20she%20could%20still%20be%20fair%2C%20and%20Glanville%20made%20sure%20other%20jurors%20who%20heard%20her%20disclosing%20the%20video%20still%20believed%20they%20could%20be%20fair%2C%20too.%20But%20jurors%20also%20aren't%20supposed%20to%20be%20researching%2C%20reading%2C%20or%20watching%20anything%20about%20the%20case%2C%20so%20Glanville%20responded%20to%20the%20woman%20finding%20the%20video%20by%20implementing%20his%20blanket%20ban%20on%20all%20social%20media%20use%20by%20jurors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20judge%20himself%20controls%20one%20of%20the%20most%20sought-after%20sightings%20for%20online%20trial%20watchers%3A%20his%20service%20dog%2C%20Jack%2C%20a%20black%20lab%20who%20joins%20Glanville%20in%20court%20each%20day%20but%20stays%20behind%20the%20bench%20and%20out%20of%20sight.%20A%20Brigadier%20General%20in%20the%20Army%20Reserve%2C%20the%20judge%20told%20The%20Atlanta%20Journal-Constitution%20that%20Jack%20helps%20with%20his%20post-traumatic%20stress%20disorder.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGlanville's%20battlefield%20experience%20led%20to%20a%20viral%20moment%20early%20in%20trial%20when%20Thug's%20lawyer%20Brian%20Steel%20was%20cross-examining%20a%20police%20officer%20about%20a%20stolen%20gun%20he%20found%20during%20a%202013%20traffic%20stop%20in%20which%20Thug%20was%20arrested.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20point%20the%20muzzle%20always%20down%2C%20no%20matter%20if%20it's%20unloaded%2C%20OK%3F%20You%20make%20everyone%20nervous%2C%20including%20Mr.%20Kerns%20who%20you%20pointed%20it%20at%2C%26quot%3B%20Glanville%20said%20referring%20to%20his%20staff%20attorney%2C%20Wesley%20Kerns.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20judge%20has%20indicated%20proper%20firearm%20handling%20could%20be%20a%20trial%20theme.%20When%20co-defendant%20Marquavius%20Huey's%20lawyer%20Careton%20Matthews%20Sr.%2C%20asked%20last%20week%20if%20he%20could%20display%20a%20firearm%20that%20had%20been%20entered%20as%20evidence%2C%20the%20judge%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20welcome%20to%20handle%20said%20firearm.%20As%20long%20as%20you%20handle%20it%20correctly.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-thug-trials-rockiest-moments-so-far-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702506829000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657a310f50edbc52a86406f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-thug-trials-rockiest-moments-so-far-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Young%20Thug%20is%20at%20the%20center%20of%20a%20sprawling%20racketeering%20and%20gang%20case%20in%20Atlanta%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20it's%20already%20full%20of%20surprising%20twists.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Meghann%20Cuniff)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-thug-trials-rockiest-moments-so-far-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Michelle%20Obama%20Hits%20CAA%20for%20Meetings%20After%20Impressive%20%E2%80%98Leave%20the%20World%20Behind%E2%80%99%20Netflix%20Debut%22%2C%22conten