to%20working%20long%20hours.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWayfair%20first%20turned%20a%20profit%20in%202020%20during%20the%20pandemic%20furniture%20boom%20before%20hitting%20headwinds.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthis-guys-company-brought-in-500-million-last-year-and-now-its-breaking-free-from-google-2012-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWayfair%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20profitable%20once%20again%20and%20%26quot%3Bback%20to%20winning%2C%26quot%3B%20its%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20Niraj%20Shah%20told%20employees%20in%20an%20email%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20employees%20should%20expect%20to%20work%20long%20hours%20and%20%26quot%3Bthink%20of%20any%20company%20money%20you%20spend%20as%20your%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20company%20is%20back%20in%20the%20green%20and%20repeat%20customers%20are%20up%2C%20Shah%20cautioned%20employees%20that%20%26quot%3Bwinning%20takes%20hard%20work%26quot%3B%20and%20they%20should%20be%20frugal%20about%20spending%20and%20open%20to%20working%20long%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWorking%20long%20hours%2C%20being%20responsive%2C%20blending%20work%20and%20life%2C%20is%20not%20anything%20to%20shy%20away%20from%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20history%20of%20laziness%20being%20rewarded%20with%20success.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20emphasize%20the%20point%2C%20Shah%20said%20he%20was%20concerned%20to%20have%20heard%20of%20some%20outdated%20or%20inaccurate%20%26quot%3BNirajisms%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20phrases%20that%20begin%20with%20%26quot%3BNiraj%20said.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20one%20I%20would%20reference%20here%20that%20I%20heard%20was%20'Niraj%20said%20that%20he%20does%20not%20think%20that%20we%20should%20work%20late'.%20I%20would%20suggest%20that%20this%20is%20laughably%20false%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BHard%20work%20is%20essential%20for%20success%2C%20and%20a%20key%20part%20of%20getting%20things%20done.%20Everyone%20deserves%20to%20have%20a%20great%20personal%20life%20%E2%80%94%20everyone%20manages%20that%20in%20their%20own%20way%20%E2%80%94%20ambitious%20people%20find%20ways%20to%20blend%20and%20balance%20the%20two.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20should%20treat%20company%20spending%20as%20their%20own%2C%20and%20negotiate%20costs%20to%20get%20the%20best%20deal%20possible%2C%20Shah%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20underline%20how%20important%20it%20was%20to%20negotiate%20every%20price%2C%20Shah%20shared%20a%20story%20about%20how%20much%20the%20company%20had%20initially%20been%20quoted%20to%20run%20some%20ethernet%20wires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20cost%20we%20were%20discussing%20yesterday%20was%20the%20cost%20to%20run%20ethernet%20wires.%20In%20this%20example%20it%20started%20at%20%241%2C600%20a%20drop.%20At%2012%20drops%20that%20would%20be%20%2419%2C200.%20To%20run%20them%20would%20take%20two%20people%20maybe%208%20hours%20or%20so.%20I%20would%20be%20happy%20to%20spend%20a%20Saturday%20doing%20this%20with%20you%20and%20splitting%20%2419%2C200.%20Basically%20that%20price%20is%20highway%20robbery.%20Why%20did%20we%20get%20robbed%3F%20Because%20no%20one%20worried%20about%20the%20cost%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThat%20%241%2C600%20became%20%24800%20and%20then%20%24300%20as%20some%20questions%20were%20asked%20and%20negotiations%20ensued.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20profitability%20milestone%20comes%20after%20the%20home-furnishing%20company%20has%20engaged%20in%20cost-cutting%20measures%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flayoffs-sweeping-the-us-these-are-the-companies-making-cuts-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elayoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20following%20recent%20losses%20after%20first%20turning%20a%20profit%20in%20early%202020.%20That%20profit%20came%20during%20the%20furniture%20boom%20of%20the%20pandemic.%20During%20its%20most%20recent%20company%20earnings%20posted%20November%201%2C%20Wayfair%20reported%20a%20loss%20of%20%24163%20million%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%2C%20which%20had%20significantly%20narrowed%20year-over-year%20from%20a%20%24283%20million%20loss%20in%20Q3%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20stock%20was%20up%20nearly%2010%25%20on%20Wednesday%20%E2%80%94%20and%20is%20up%20nearly%2074%25%20so%20far%20this%20year.%20Still%2C%20over%20five%20years%20it's%20down%2045%25%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20broader%20stock%20market%2C%20which%20is%20up%2081%25%20over%20the%20same%20time%20frame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20incredibly%20proud%20of%20our%20world-class%20team%20and%20culture%20of%20open%20communication%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Wayfair%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BIn%20his%20note%2C%20Niraj%20was%20reinforcing%20some%20of%20the%20values%20that%20have%20contributed%20to%20Wayfair's%20success%2C%20including%20questioning%20the%20status%20quo%2C%20being%20cost-efficient%20and%20working%20hard%20together%20to%20drive%20results.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20the%20full%20text%20of%20Niraj%20Shah's%20email%20to%20Wayfair%20employees%20below%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHi%20everyone%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20thought%20I%20would%20take%20a%20minute%20to%20share%20some%20thoughts%20that%20I%20have%20had%20recently.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20we%20work%20our%20way%20through%20the%20holiday%20season%20it%20is%20really%20encouraging%20to%20see%20that%20we%20are%20back%20to%20winning.%20Winning%20feels%20good%20-%20and%20is%20a%20great%20reward%20for%20all%20of%20our%20efforts.%20Our%20market%20share%20is%20growing%20nicely%2C%20our%20repeat%20is%20increasing%2C%20our%20suppliers%20are%20leaning%20in%2C%20and%20we%20are%20profitable.%20This%20is%20something%20to%20be%20very%20proud%20of.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThat%20said%2C%20while%20we%20have%20worked%20hard%20to%20get%20back%20to%20the%20execution%20oriented%2C%20hard%20working%2C%20frugal%2C%20customer%20oriented%20culture%20that%20we%20had%20for%20most%20of%20our%20history%20we%20still%20have%20some%20work%20to%20do%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20we%20get%20fully%20back.%20And%20this%20is%20what%20I%20want%20us%20all%20to%20push%20on%20in%20the%20weeks%20and%20months%20to%20come.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOne%20point%20I%20think%20is%20important%20to%20make%20is%20that%20winning%20requires%20hard%20work.%20I%20believe%20that%20most%20of%20us%2C%20being%20ambitious%20individuals%2C%20find%20fulfillment%20in%20the%20joy%20of%20seeing%20our%20efforts%20materialize%20into%20tangible%20results.%20Working%20long%20hours%2C%20being%20responsive%2C%20blending%20work%20and%20life%2C%20is%20not%20anything%20to%20shy%20away%20from.%20There%20is%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20history%20of%20laziness%20being%20rewarded%20with%20success.%20Hard%20work%20is%20an%20essential%20ingredient%20in%20any%20recipe%20for%20success.%20I%20embrace%20this%2C%20and%20the%20most%20successful%20people%20I%20know%20do%20as%20well.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20may%20know%20of%20Nirajisms%2C%20these%20are%20phrases%20that%20start%20with%20'Niraj%20said'.%20What%20disappoints%20me%20is%20that%20the%20majority%20I%20hear%20are%20either%20not%20true%2C%20are%20old%20and%20no%20longer%20applicable%2C%20or%20are%20taken%20out%20of%20context.%20The%20one%20I%20would%20reference%20here%20that%20I%20heard%20was%20'Niraj%20said%20that%20he%20does%20not%20think%20that%20we%20should%20work%20late'.%20I%20would%20suggest%20that%20this%20is%20laughably%20false.%20Hard%20work%20is%20essential%20for%20success%2C%20and%20a%20key%20part%20of%20getting%20things%20done.%20Everyone%20deserves%20to%20have%20a%20great%20personal%20life%20-%20everyone%20manages%20that%20in%20their%20own%20way%20-%20ambitious%20people%20find%20ways%20to%20blend%20and%20balance%20the%20two.%20I%20think%20that%20is%20what%20we%20all%20should%20do.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20heard%20another%20Nirajism%20yesterday%20which%20was%20'Niraj%20said%20that%20we%20cannot%20recruit%20from%20Google%20Amazon%20or%20Walmart'.%20I%20am%20not%20even%20sure%20where%20that%20could%20come%20from%20since%20so%20many%20of%20our%20senior%20leaders%20are%20from%20these%20places.%20Again%20false.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20would%20encourage%20you%20to%20run%20any%20Nirajism%20that%20sounds%20odd%20by%20me.%20I%20am%20happy%20to%20clarify%20anything.%20And%20I%20am%20sure%20there%20are%20some%20that%20in%20fact%20I%20would%20support%20and%20say%20we%20should%20stick%20with.%20Ultimately%20I%20want%20us%20to%20be%20aggressive%2C%20pragmatic%2C%20frugal%2C%20agile%2C%20customer%20oriented%2C%20and%20smart.%20Use%20those%20as%20filters%20and%20I%20think%20things%20can%20become%20clearer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20would%20also%20encourage%20you%20to%20think%20of%20any%20company%20money%20you%20spend%20as%20your%20own.%20Would%20you%20spend%20money%20on%20that%2C%20would%20you%20spend%20that%20much%20money%20for%20that%20thing%2C%20does%20that%20price%20seem%20reasonable%2C%20and%20lastly%20-%20have%20you%20negotiated%20the%20price%3F%20Everything%20is%20negotiable%20and%20so%20if%20you%20haven't%20then%20you%20should%20start%20there.%20One%20cost%20we%20were%20discussing%20yesterday%20was%20the%20cost%20to%20run%20ethernet%20wires.%20In%20this%20example%20it%20started%20at%20%241%2C600%20a%20drop.%20At%2012%20drops%20that%20would%20be%20%2419%2C200.%20To%20run%20them%20would%20take%20two%20people%20maybe%208%20hours%20or%20so.%20I%20would%20be%20happy%20to%20spend%20a%20Saturday%20doing%20this%20with%20you%20and%20splitting%20%2419%2C200.%20Basically%20that%20price%20is%20highway%20robbery.%20Why%20did%20we%20get%20robbed%3F%20Because%20no%20one%20worried%20about%20the%20cost.%20That%20%241%2C600%20became%20%24800%20and%20then%20%24300%20as%20some%20questions%20were%20asked%20and%20nego