t%20help%20but%20notice%20a%20familiar%20title%20in%20the%20Top%20100%20most%20watched%20shows%3A%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3ECocomelon%3A%20Season%201%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20No.%2061.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20shocked%20mainly%20to%20discover%20that%20%26quot%3BCocomelon%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20generally%20plot-free%20collection%20of%20animated%20nursery%20rhymes%20for%20babies%20and%20toddlers%20that%20started%20as%20YouTube%20videos%2C%20has%20%26quot%3Bseasons%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it%20turns%20out%20that%20there%20are%20actually%20six%20of%20them%20on%20Netflix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20say%20you%20combine%20the%20watch%20time%20of%20all%20six%20seasons%2C%20which%20seems%20fair%20since%20it's%20hard%20to%20argue%20that%20any%202-year-old%20is%20clamoring%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20newest%20season%20to%20follow%20up%20on%20the%20cliffhangers%20presented%20in%20%26quot%3BWheels%20on%20the%20Bus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECombined%2C%20%26quot%3BCocomelon%26quot%3B%20(Seasons%201-6)%20was%20watched%20on%20Netflix%20for%20601%20million%20hours%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202023%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYes%2C%20601%20million%20hours.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20stuff%20like%20this%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FohHYABXMqUQ%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Yes%20Yes%20Vegetables%20Song%20%7C%20%40CoComelon%20Nursery%20Rhymes%20%26amp%3B%20Kids%20Songs%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20more%20than%20all%20four%20seasons%20of%20%26quot%3BStranger%20Things%26quot%3B%20combined%20that%20were%20watched%20during%20the%20same%20time%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20ranked%20the%20combined%20%26quot%3BCocomelon%26quot%3B%20next%20to%20the%20other%20shows%