te.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_090117_best-kitchenaid-mixers-20%26h%3D68465b0cb43fbaa6c6714c8c5195b1523f45598070be705a97e04062bb3d5696%26postID%3D61b8efc6f2a36b1ac9f415cc%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbest-kitchenaid%26site%3Din%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.kitchenaid.com%252F100year%252Fhistory.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20KitchenAid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20brand%20got%20its%20name%20in%201919%20when%20an%20executive's%20wife%20called%20the%20first%20home%20model%20stand%20mixer%20%26quot%3Bthe%20best%20kitchen%20aid%20I've%20ever%20had.%26quot%3B%20The%20name%20stuck%20and%20KitchenAid%20has%20been%20synonymous%20with%20stand%20mixers%20ever%20since.%20While%20there%20are%20a%20number%20of%20great%20stand%20mixers%20from%20other%20brands%20out%20there%2C%20KitchenAid%20still%20stands%20out%20in%20a%20number%20of%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I've%20tried%20almost%20every%20brand%20of%20stand%20mixer%20out%20there%20in%20my%20seven%20years%20reviewing%20kitchen%20products%2C%20and%20KitchenAid%20mixers%20are%20the%20only%20ones%20that%20use%20an%20almost%20all-metal%20construction.%20Other%20brands%20cut%20costs%20by%20using%20plastic%20in%20part%20of%20the%20design%3A%20either%20in%20the%20body%20of%20the%20mixer%2C%20on%20knobs%20and%20dials%2C%20in%20the%20mixing%20attachments%2C%20or%20even%20in%20the%20gears.%20Mixers%20made%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20plastic%20are%20usually%20lighter%20and%20less%20expensive%2C%20but%20much%20less%20durable.%20KitchenAid%20mixers%20can%20last%20for%20decades%20because%20of%20their%20strong%20metal%20parts.%20While%20this%20stronger%20construction%20comes%20at%20a%20premium%20%E2%80%94%20KitchenAid%20mixers%20are%20among%20the%20most%20expensive%20out%20there%20%E2%80%94%20their%20durability%20makes%20them%20a%20great%20investment.%20Even%20the%20most%20affordable%20KitchenAid%20mixer%20shares%20this%20same%20hearty%20construction%20and%20powerful