air%20straightener%20in%20light%20blue.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61aa502c35814a00195e78b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBaBylissPRo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20quick%20Google%20search%2C%20you'll%20find%20that%20this%20design%20by%20BaBylissPRO%20has%20racked%20up%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20positive%20reviews%20across%20retail%20sites%20such%20as%20Amazon%2C%20Ulta%2C%20and%20Bed%20Bath%20%26amp%3B%20Beyond.%20But%20one%20of%20the%20strongest%20reviews%20comes%20from%20Everett.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20go-to%20iron%20for%20straightening%20curly%20and%20coily%20hair%20and%20creating%20silk%20press%20styles%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%2C%20calling%20out%20the%20iron%20which%20makes%20it%20%26quot%3Beasy%20to%20straighten%20hair%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20scalp.%26quot%3B%20While%20Everett%20uses%20this%20product%20for%20creating%20smooth%2C%20straight%20results%2C%20she%20says%20it's%20multifunctional%2C%20too.%20%26quot%3BThe%20thin%20plates%20also%20make%20this%20iron%20great%20for%20creating%20waves%20and%20curls.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20curling%20hair%3A%20GHD%20Platinum%2B%20Styler%20-%201%26quot%3B%20Flat%20Iron%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22GHD%20Platinum%2B%20Styler%20-%201%26quot%3B%20Flat%20Iron%20in%20black%20and%20white.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61aa524635814a00195e7a01%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGHD%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20definitely%20on%20the%20pricier%20side%20but%20well%20worth%20it%20if%20you%20use%20a%20flat%20iron%20daily%2C%26quot%3B%20Jessica%20Page%20says%20about%20the%20GHD%20Platinum%2B%20Styler.%20For%20this%20salon%20owner%2C%20a%20styling%20tool%20with%20as%20many%20features%20as%20this%20one%20has%20proven%20itself%20to%20be%20a%20gem.%20Designed%20with%20the%20latest%20technology%2C%20this%20flat%20iron%20guarantees%20even%20heat%20across%20the%20plate%2C%20has%20universal%20voltage%20great%20for%20traveling%2C%20and%20has%20a%20sleep%20mode%20that%20turns%20itself%20off%20when%20you%20forget%20to.%20Page%20has%20the%20circumference%20of%20the%20iron%20to%20thank%20for%20its%20ability%20to%20create%20a%20curl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20curling%20your%20hair%20with%20a%20straightener%2C%20she%20suggests%20separating%20hair%20into%20two%20sections%20to%20start.%20%26quot%3BClamp%20the%20flat%20iron%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20section%2C%20turn%20the%20flat%20iron%20360%20degrees%2C%20and%20pull%20the%20flat%20iron%20down%20the%20section%20with%20smooth%2C%20consistent%20timing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20recommends.%20%26quot%3BThis%20helps%20to%20avoid%20creasing!%20After%20the%20flat%20iron%20has%20passed%20through%20the%20section%2C%20immediately%20twist%20the%20curl%20in%20the%20same%20direction%20you%20curled%20it%20with%20your%20finger.%20Allow%20the%20section%20to%20curl%20before%20brushing%20to%20ensure%20the%20curl%20lasts%20as%20long%20as%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20customization%3A%20T3%20Smooth%20ID%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22T3%20Smooth%20ID%20flat%20iron%20in%20white%20and%20rose%20gold.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61aa4f9835814a00195e7893%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ET3%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20celebrity%20extension%20expert%20Valles%2C%20one%20of%20her%20favorite%20straighteners%20also%20happens%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20advanced%20options.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20great%20because%20it%20allows%20you%20to%20customize%20your%20texture%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Valles%2C%20referencing%20the%20devices'%20Smooth%20ID%20which%20adjusts%20the%20settings%20to%20best%