author%22%3A%22VISHWA%20MOHAN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Home%20Ministry%20Orders%20Probe%20Into%20Parliament%20Security%20Breach%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20has%20ordered%20an%20inquiry%20into%20today's%20parliament%20security%20breach.%20A%20committee%20has%20been%20set%20up%20under%20Anish%20Dayal%20Singh%2C%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20the%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Forces%2C%20with%20members%20from%20other%20security%20agencies%20and%20experts.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20the%20ministry%20said%20the%20committee%20will%20investigate%20the%20reasons%20for%20breach%20in%20security%2C%20identify%20lapses%20and%20recommend%20further%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20submit%20its%20report%20with%20recommendations%2C%20including%20suggestions%20on%20improving%20security%20in%20Parliament%2C%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20afternoon%2C%20two%20men%20had%20carried%20in%20yellow%20canisters%20evading%20all%20security.%20During%20the%20parliament%20proceedings%2C%20one%20of%20them%20jumped%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20floor%20from%20the%20visitors'%20gallery%20and%20activated%20the%20canisters%2C%20releasing%20thick%20yellow%20smoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20breach%20took%20place%20despite%20upgraded%20security%20at%20the%20new%20parliament%2C%20triggering%20a%20flood%20of%20questions%20on%20lapses%20and%20loopholes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20multi-layered%20security%20around%20the%20building%20involves%20background%20checks%2C%20manual%20frisking%2C%20baggage%20check-in%20and%20other%20processes%20conducted%20by%20multiple%20agencies%20including%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20and%20the%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Forces.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThere%20is%20suspicion%20that%20the%20men%20had%20hid%20the%20yellow%20smoke%20canisters%20inside%20their%20shoes%2C%20which%20security%20personnel%20frisking%20them%20must%20have%20missed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%20demanded%20that%20Prathap%20Simha%2C%20the%20BJP%20MP%20who%20signed%20the%20pass%20request%20for%20men%20who%20breached%20parliament%20security%2C%20be%20questioned.%20They%20have%20declared%20the%20security%20breach%20a%20terrorist%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20arrested%20five%20persons%20%E2%80%93%20two%20from%20them%20from%20inside%20parliament%20and%20two%20from%20outside.%20Another%20person%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20traced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManoranjan%20D%20and%20Sagar%20Sharma%20were%20the%20two%20who%20had%20got%20into%20the%20visitors'%20gallery.%20Two%20others%2C%20Amol%20Shinde%20and%20Neelam%20Devi%2C%20were%20detained%20from%20outside%20Parliament.%20They%20were%20carrying%20coloured%20smoke%20canisters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreliminary%20investigation%20has%20indicated%20that%20the%20four%20people%20who%20went%20to%20parliament%20today%20do%20not%20belong%20to%20any%20terror%20group.%20Sources%20said%20the%20chances%20are%20that%20they%20had%20self-radicalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702488360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F3hpmuhho_parliament-security-breach-_625x300_13_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhome-ministry-orders-probe-into-parliament-security-breach-4668549%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20has%20ordered%20an%20inquiry%20into%20today's%20parliament%20security%20breach.%20A%20committee%20has%20been%20set%20up%20under%20Anish%20Dayal%20Singh%2C%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20the%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Forces%2C%20with%20members%20from%20other%20security%20agencies%20and%20expe%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhome-ministry-orders-probe