ustry%20has%20lodged%20a%20formal%20complaint%20against%20actor%20Darshan%20Jariwala%20at%20a%20Kolkata%20police%20station.%20Taking%20to%20social%20media%2C%20she%20publicly%20announced%20the%20filing%20of%20the%20complaint%20and%20has%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20CINTAA%20(Cine%20And%20TV%20Artistes'%20Association)%20seeking%20their%20intervention%20in%20the%20matter%20for%20justice.%20The%20complainant%20shared%20details%20of%20her%20relationship%20with%20Jariwala%2C%20claiming%20they%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bgandharv%20vivaah%26quot%3B%20and%20she%20is%20currently%20carrying%20his%20child.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmedia-professional-files-complaint-against-actor-darshan-jariwala-seeks-cintaas-intervention%2Farticleshow%2F105969671.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gaza%20War%20To%20Continue%20%26quot%3BWith%20Or%20Without%20International%20Support%26quot%3B%3A%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsrael%20declared%20on%20Wednesday%20its%20determination%20to%20continue%20its%20Gaza%20war%20%26quot%3Bwith%20or%20without%20international%20support%26quot%3B%2C%20after%20it%20came%20under%20mounting%20pressure%20even%20from%20key%20backer%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20in%20its%20third%20month%2C%20the%20war%20was%20launched%20in%20response%20to%20the%20unprecedented%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20by%20Palestinian%20militant%20group%20Hamas%20on%20October%207%20that%20Israeli%20officials%20say%20killed%201%2C200%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20left%20Gaza%20in%20ruins%2C%20killing%20more%20than%2018%2C600%20people%2C%20mostly%20women%20and%20children%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20toll%20from%20the%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry%2C%20and%20causing%20%26quot%3Bunparallelled%26quot%3B%20damage%20to%20its%20roads%2C%20schools%20and%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20overwhelmingly%20backed%20a%20non-binding%20resolution%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20more%20air%20strikes%20hit%20Gaza%20and%20gun%20battles%20raged%2C%20especially%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%20the%20biggest%20urban%20centre%2C%20and%20Khan%20Yunis%20and%20Rafah%20in%20the%20south%2C%20AFP%20correspondents%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECold%20autumn%20rains%20lashed%20the%20territory%2C%20where%20millions%20have%20been%20displaced%20and%20many%20are%20living%20in%20makeshift%20plastic%20tents%2C%20as%20vital%20supplies%20of%20food%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20medicines%20and%20fuel%20have%20run%20low%20in%20more%20than%20two%20months%20of%20siege%20and%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECamped%20with%20thousands%20of%20others%20in%20the%20grounds%20of%20the%20Al-Aqsa%20Martyrs%20hospital%20in%20central%20Gaza%2C%20Ameen%20Edwan%20said%20his%20family%20was%20unable%20to%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRainwater%20seeped%20in.%20We%20couldn't%20sleep.%20We%20tried%20to%20find%20nylon%20covers%20but%20couldn't%20find%20any%2C%20so%20we%20resorted%20to%20stones%20and%20sand%26quot%3B%20to%20keep%20the%20rain%20out%2C%20he%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20raid%20sirens%20wailed%20in%20Sderot%20and%20other%20southern%20Israeli%20communities%20near%20Gaza%20as%20Palestinian%20militants%20kept%20firing%20rockets%2C%20most%20of%20which%20have%20been%20intercepted%20by%20air%20defences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20said%20sirens%20sounded%20in%20Ashdod%20city%20north%20of%20Gaza%20and%20in%20the%20Lakhish%20area.%20Social%20media%20footage%20showed%20a%20large%20fragment%20of%20an%20intercepted%20rocket%20had%20hit%20a%20supermarket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20said%20an%20air%20strike%20had%20hit%20a%20militant%20cell%20in%20Gaza%20City's%20Shejaiya%20district%20%26quot%3Bthat%20was%20en%20route%20to%20launch%20rockets%20toward%20Israel%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Khan%20Yunis%2C%20a%20centre%20of%20heavy%20urban%20combat%20in%20recent%20days%2C%20a%20family%20gathered%20to%20mourn%20the%20death%20in%20a%20strike%20of%20Fayez%20al-Taramsi%2C%20a%20father%20of%20seven.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20are%20we%20going%20to%20live%20after%20him%3F%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20his%20daughters%20said%2C%20crying%20and%20clutching%20his%20bloodied%20shirt.%20%26quot%3BHe%20brought%20us%20to%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bloodiest-ever%20Gaza%20war%20broke%20out%20after%20Hamas%20gunmen%20attacked%20Israel%20on%20October%207%20--%20the%20deadliest%20in%20the%20country's%2075-year%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20seized%20around%20240%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%2C%20determined%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%20and%20bring%20the%20hostages%20home%2C%20launched%20a%20devastating%20aerial%20and%20ground%20offensive%20on%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20says%20it%20has%20lost%20115%20soldiers%2C%20including%2010%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20its%20deadliest%20day%20since%20launching%20the%20ground%20assault%20on%20October%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Diminishing%20safe%20space'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20passed%20a%20resolution%20Tuesday%20demanding%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20backed%20by%20153%20of%20193%20nations%20--%20surpassing%20the%20140%20or%20so%20that%20have%20routinely%20condemned%20Russia%20for%20invading%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20United%20States%20voted%20against%20the%20resolution%2C%20it%20was%20supported%20by%20allies%20Australia%2C%20Canada%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20who%2C%20in%20a%20rare%20joint%20statement%2C%20said%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Balarmed%20at%20the%20diminishing%20safe%20space%20for%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20told%20a%20campaign%20event%20that%20Israel%20had%20%26quot%3Bmost%20of%20the%20world%20supporting%20it%26quot%3B%20immediately%20after%20the%20October%207%20attack%2C%20but%20that%20%26quot%3Bthey're%20starting%20to%20lose%20that%20support%20by%20the%20indiscriminate%20bombing%20that%20takes%20place%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20leader%2C%20who%20toned%20down%20his%20comments%20later%2C%20on%20Wednesday%20met%20with%20families%20of%20American%20hostages%20from%20among%20those%20the%20militants%20seized%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20criticism%20from%20its%20main%20ally%2C%20Israel%20vowed%20to%20press%20on%20with%20its%20war%20on%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsrael%20will%20continue%20the%20war%20against%20Hamas%20with%20or%20without%20international%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Foreign%20Minister%20Eli%20Cohen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20ceasefire%20at%20the%20current%20stage%20is%20a%20gift%20to%20the%20terrorist%20organisation%20Hamas%2C%20and%20will%20allow%20it%20to%20return%20and%20threaten%20the%20residents%20of%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohen%20told%20a%20visiting%20diplomat%2C%20quoted%20by%20his%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20national%20security%20advisor%2C%20Jake%20Sullivan%2C%20will%20travel%20to%20Israel%20on%20Thursday%20to%20meet%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20who%20has%20said%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bdisagreement%26quot%3B%20with%20Washington%20over%20how%20a%20post-conflict%20Gaza%20would%20be%20governed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Gaza%20City%20hospital%20raid%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20vote%20came%20as%20Philippe%20Lazzarini%2C%20head%20of%20its%20Palestinian%20refugee%20agency%2C%20said%20Gazans%20were%20%26quot%3Brunning%20out%20of%20time%20and%20options%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20estimates%201.9%20million%20of%20the%20territory's%202.4%20million%20people%20have%20been%20displaced%20and%20are%20receiving%20goods%20from%20only%20around%20100%20aid%20trucks%20per%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20hospital%20system%20is%20in%20ruins%2C%20and%20Hamas%20authorities%20said%20Wednesday%20that%20vaccines%20for%20children%20had%20run%20out%2C%20warning%20of%20%26quot%3Bcatastrophic%20health%20repercussions%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUN%20satellite%20analysis%20agency%20UNOSAT%20said%20Tuesday%20that%2018%20percent%20of%20Gaza's%20infrastructure%20had%20been%20destroyed%2C%20based%20on%20an%20image%20that%20was%20already%20more%20than%20two%20weeks%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Bank%20in%20a%20new%20analysis%20warned%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20loss%20of%20life%2C%20speed%20and%20extent%20of%20damages...%20are%20unparallelled%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlready%20by%20mid-November%2C%20almost%20half%20of%20all%20roads%20and%20around%2060%20percent%20of%20communication%20infrastructure%2C%20health%20and%20education%20facilities%20had%20been%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20said%20Israeli%20forces%20raided%20a%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20City%20on%20Tuesday.%20UN%20humanitarian%20agency%20OCHA%20had%20earlier%20reported%20fighting%20nearby%20and%20said%20about%203%2C000%20displaced%20people%20were%20trapped%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20did%20not%20comment%2C%20but%20Israel%20has%20repeatedly%20accused%20Hamas%20of%20using%20hospitals%2C%20schools%2C%20mosques%20and%20vast%20tunnel%20systems%20beneath%20them%20as%20military%20bases%20--%20claims%20the%20group%20has%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20World%20Health%20Organization's%20chief%20Tedros%20Adhanom%20Ghebreyesus%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20worried%26quot%3B%20by%20reports%20of%20the%20raid%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20agency%20%26quot%3Burgently%20calls%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20all%20persons%20inside%20the%20hospital%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFears%20of%20a%20wider%20conflict%20continued%20to%20grow%2C%20with%20daily%20exchanges%20of%20fire%20along%20Israel's%20border%20with%20Lebanon%2C%20where%20Hezbollah%20is%20based%2C%20and%20other%20Iran-backed%20groups%20targeting%20US%20and%20allied%