rations%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20since%20March%202023%20to%20address%20the%20Pune%20bypoll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20quashed%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20certificate%20stating%20that%20by-polls%20will%20not%20be%20held%20as%20the%20poll%20panel%20is%20%E2%80%9Cbusy%20with%20preparation%20for%202024%20General%20Elections%20and%20the%20candidate%20elected%20in%20the%20bye-election%20will%20have%20a%20very%20short%20tenure%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fhigh-court%2Fbombay-high-court%2Fbombay-high-court-directs-eci-hold-pune-lok-sabha-bye-election-244454%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20observed%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2211%5C%22%3EIn%20any%20parliamentary%20democracy%2C%20governance%20is%20elected%20representatives%20who%20are%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20people.%20If%20a%20representative%20is%20no%20more%2C%20another%20must%20be%20put%20in%20place.%20The%20people%20cannot%20go%20unrepresented.%20That%20is%20wholly%20unconstitutional%20and%20is%20fundamental%20anathema%20to%20our%20constitutional%20structure.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CBusiness%20of%20ECI%20staff%20cannot%20result%20in%20citizens%20going%20unrepresented%20and%20that%20is%20unthinkable%20and%20it%20would%20amount%20to%20sabotaging%20entire%20constitutional%20framework%2C%20which%20we%20trust%20that%20is%20what%20even%20ECI%20did%20not%20want%E2%80%A6.%20In%20any%20parliamentary%20democracy%2C%20governance%20is%20done%20by%20elected%20representatives%20who%20are%20the%20voices%20of%20people.%20If%20a%20representative%20is%20no%20more%2C%20another%20must%20be%20put%20in%20place.%20People%20cannot%20go%20unrepresented.%20That%20is%20wholly%20unconstitutional%20and%20is%20fundamental%20anathema%20to%20constitutional%20structure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20division%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Patel%20and%20Justice%20Kamal%20R.%20Khata%20was%20hearing%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20Pune%20resident%20Sughosh%20Joshi%20challenging%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20decision%20not%20to%20hold%20elections%20until%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Section%20151A%20of%20the%20Representation%20of%20People%20Act%2C%201951%2C%20the%20vacancy%20should%20be%20filled%20through%20a%20bypoll%20within%20six%20months%2C%20or%20by%20September%2028%20in%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20ECI%20invoked%20Section%20151A%20(b)%20of%20the%20Act%20in%20August%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20two%20exceptions%20to%20the%20this%20rule.%20The%C2%A0exception%20says%20that%20the%20ECI%20in%20consultation%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20can%20certify%20that%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20hold%20the%20by-election%20within%20the%20said%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoshi%20contended%20that%20the%20constituents%20had%20been%20without%20a%20voice%20in%20parliament%20for%20several%20months%2C%20particularly%20concerning%20significant%20delays%20in%20various%20development%20projects%20in%20Pune.%20The%20high%20court%2C%20on%20December%207%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbombay-hc-delay-pune-by-poll-ec-satisfactory-response%5C%22%3Eexpressed%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20preliminary%20disagreement%20with%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20reasoning%20that%20holding%20bypolls%20would%20disrupt%20both%20the%20tenure%20of%20the%20returned%20candidate%20and%20preparations%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20ECI%20had%20announced%20by-elections%20for%20seven%20assembly%20seats%20in%20August%20but%20not%20for%20the%20Pune%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702480191000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15095822%2F5464294256_b5f0c9d577_k.jpg%22%2C%22ori