n%20the%20video%20was%20not%20him%20but%20a%20deepfake.%20''And%20in%20this%20video%2C%20it%20isn't%20me%3B%20it%20is%20my%20deep%20fake%20AI%20avatar%2C''%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20the%20video%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20rise%20of%20AI%20technology%20and%20deepfakes%20pose%20a%20large%20risk%20to%20the%20financial%20services%20industry.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20tipping%20point%20for%20Indian%20financial%20services%20businesses%20was%20when%20onboarding%20became%20completely%20digital%2C%20thanks%20to%20Aadhaar%2C%20etc.%20For%20businesses%20onboarding%20a%20new%20customer%2C%20an%20important%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FDI9Z1Q3jxY%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FDI9Z1Q3jxY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Nithin%20Kamath%20(%40Nithin0dha)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNithin0dha%2Fstatus%2F1734859356959539524%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20internet%20users%20were%20left%20stunned%20and%20said%20that%20they%20didn't%20realise%20that%20it%20was%20not%20Mr%20Kamath%20speaking%20but%20a%20deepfake.%20One%20user%20said%2C%20''The%20last%20bit%20was%20a%20jaw-dropping%20moment.''%20Another%20wrote%2C%20''The%20last%20line%20was%20the%20killing%20note.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20few%20people%20figured%20out%20that%20something%20was%20wrong%20with%20the%20video.%20Another%20added%2C%20''It%20seemed%20so%20deepfake%2C%20otherwise%20u%20are%20a%20smiley%20person%20and%20that%20wasn't%20there%20throughout%20the%20video.''%20A%20fourth%20wrote%2C%20''Yeah%2C%20figured%20it%20wasn't%20you.%20Lip%20sync%2C%20expressions%2C%20eyes%2C%20no%20laughter%2C%20no%20fumbling%2C%20and%20no%20pauses%20(had%20watched%20your%20and%20your%20wife's%20interview%20last%20night.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20a%20deepfake%20is%20a%20type%20of%20synthetic%20media%20that%20uses%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20manipulate%20or%20generate%20visual%20and%20audio%20content%2C%20often%20with%20a%20malicious%20motive%2C%20to%20appear%20authentic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepfakes%2C%20a%20potent%20blend%20of%20real%20and%20fabricated%20media%2C%20have%20emerged%20as%20a%20formidable%20threat%20to%20public%20trust%20and%20truth.%20By%20creating%20convincing%20videos%20and%20audio%20recordings%20of%20people%20saying%20or%20doing%20things%20they%20never%20did%2C%20deepfakes%20can%20manipulate%20public%20perception%2C%20spread%20misinformation%2C%20and%20tarnish%20reputations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20several%20'deepfake'%20videos%20targeting%20celebrities%20like%20Rashmika%20Mandanna%2C%20Katrina%20Kaif%2C%20Kajol%2C%20and%C2%A0Ratan%20Tata%20went%C2%A0viral%2C%20sparking%20public%20outrage%20and%20raising%20c%20oncerns%20over%20the%20misuse%20of%20technology%20and%20tools%20for%20creating%20doctored%20content%20and%20fake%20narratives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%C2%A0Union%20Minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20met%20social%20media%20platforms%20to%20review%20progress%20made%20by%20them%20in%20tackling%20misinformation%20and%20deepfakes%20and%20asserted%20that%20advisories%20will%20be%20issued%20to%20ensure%20100%20per%20cent%20compliance%20by%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702473420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F66atovm8_nithin-kamath-deepfake_625x300_13_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fit-isnt-me-zerodhas-nithin-kamath-shares-his-own-deepfake-video-to-highlight-its-dangers-4667062%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20internet%20users%20were%20left%20stunned%20and%20said%20that%20they%20didn't%20realise%20that%20it%20was%20not%20Mr%20Kamath%20speaking%20but%20a%20deepfake.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2