%2Ffood-prices-drive-november-inflation-to-3-month-high-october-iip-at-16-month-peak-9065674%2F%5C%22%3Emeasured%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Index%20of%20Industrial%20Production%20(IIP)%2C%20rose%20to%20a%2016-month%20high%20of%2011.7%25%20in%20October%2C%20over%20a%20boost%20in%20mining%2C%20manufacturing%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702471031000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15171005%2F1024px-Supermarket_full_of_goods.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fretail-inflation-rises-to-5-55-in-november%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20is%20likely%20caused%20by%20food%20price%20increase.%20Since%20August%2C%20inflation%20had%20been%20on%20a%20decline.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fretail-inflation-rises-to-5-55-in-november%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pranab%20Mukherjee%E2%80%99s%20Daughter%E2%80%99s%20Account%20of%20His%20Diary%20'Eats%20and%20Breathes%20Politics'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F31203418%2Fpranab-mukherjee.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAnybody%20who%20interacted%20with%20Pranab%20Mukherjee%20during%20one%20of%20his%20informal%20interactions%2C%20either%20as%20the%20First%20Citizen%20or%20in%20his%20numerous%20avatars%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%2C%20is%20familiar%20with%20his%20response%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20written%20in%20my%20diary%20but%20the%20content%20will%20not%20be%20known%20during%20my%20lifetime%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%20so%20in%20one%20form%2Flanguage%20or%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20384px)%2085vw%2C%20384px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13170549%2F81afLFXd0mL._SL1500_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22384%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13170549%2F81afLFXd0mL._SL1500_.jpg%20784w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13170549%2F81afLFXd0mL._SL1500_-196x300.jpg%20196w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13170549%2F81afLFXd0mL._SL1500_-669x1024.jpg%20669w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689064%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22588%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESharmistha%20Mukherjee%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EPranab%2C%20My%20Father%3A%20A%20Daughter%20Remembers%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3ERupa%20Publications%20(December%202023)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20why%20%3Cem%3EPranab%2C%20My%20Father%3A%20A%20Daughter%20Remembers%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20such%20an%20important%20book.%20It%20brings%20to%20the%20fore%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20observations%20and%20apprehensions%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20respected%20and%20astute%20politician%20while%20infusing%20what%20is%20essentially%20a%20crucial%20piece%20of%20Indian%20history%20with%20honesty%2C%20spontaneity%2C%20and%20welcome%20wit%20that%20are%20hallmarks%20of%20the%20daughter%20%E2%80%93%20Sharmistha%20Mukherjee.%C2%A0From%20spurning%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20cryptic%20offer%20for%20the%20Jangipur%20seat%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ELodbi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(will%20you%20fight)%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20to%20becoming%20a%20Congress%20politician%20after%20her%20father%20asked%20her%20if%20she%20wanted%20to%20become%20one%20and%20then%20starting%20veritably%20from%20the%20bottom%20to%20quit%20it%20all%20and%20now%20to%20write%20this%20book%20that%20has%20created%20a%20mini%20political%20storm%20in%20a%20teacup%20over%20Mukherjee%E2%80%99s%20observations%20about%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Sharmistha%20has%20travelled%20some%20distance%2C%20her%20brief%20political%20sojourn%20notwithstanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20had%20kings%20holding%20umbrellas%20for%20her%20(then%20Bhutan%20king%20Jigme%20Singye%20Wangchuk)%2C%20and%20the%20man%20who%20her%20father%20thought%20was%20the%20only%20prime%20minister%20of%20the%20county%20after%20Indira%20Gandhi%20with%20his%20hand%20on%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20pulse%20%E2%80%93%20Narendra%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20honouring%20her%20impromptu%20dance%20programme%20invites%20and%20giving%20her%20appointments%20to%20talk%20about%20life%20and%20politics%20in%20general.%20The%20stories%20flow%20thick%20and%20fast%20along%20with%20extracts%20from%20the%20valuable%20diaries%20(tomes%20that%20even%20she%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20read%20during%20his%20lifetime%2C%20as%20she%20mentioned%20during%20the%20launch%20event%20earlier%20this%20week).%20What%20one%20misses%20in%20those%20pages%20are%20indications%20about%20her%20own%20equation%20with%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20party%20%E2%80%93%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20she%20briefly%20served%20and%20is%20often%20left%20wondering%20whether%20those%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20(PMO)%20meetings%20have%20outlived%20the%20greatest%20prime%20minister%20India%20never%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20in%20a%20sense%20eats%20and%20breathes%20politics%20but%20is%20a%20must-read%20not%20just%20for%20students%20of%20politics%20or%20history.%20It%20is%20a%20breezy%20and%20enjoyable%20read%2C%20an%20honest%20account%2C%20at%20least%20in%20the%20first%20part%20(before%20politics%20eclipsed%20the%20personal%20in%20Pranab%E2%80%99s%20life)%20as%20much%20of%20the%20young%20man%20who%20quickly%20became%20among%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20most%20trusted%20lieutenants%20as%20of%20Geeta%20(Pranab%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Subhra)%20%E2%80%93%20the%20woman%20who%20stood%20surety%20for%20one%20prime%20minister%20(P.V.%20Narasimha%20Rao)%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwept%20uncontrollably%E2%80%9D%20for%20another%20(Indira%20Gandhi)%20and%20at%20whose%20funeral%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20another%20country%20(Sheikh%20Hasina)%20could%20not%20hold%20back%20her%20tears.%20Even%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20pets%20feature%20prominently%20%E2%80%93%20from%20the%20one%20who%20bit%20a%20future%20prime%20minister%20to%20the%20one%20that%20bit%20the%20master%20during%20one%20of%20the%20lowest%20points%20of%20his%20life%20%E2%80%93%20when%20he%20was%20left%20out%20of%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20cabinet%20in%201984.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20rarely%20is%20there%20a%20book%20that%20has%20politics%20at%20its%20core%20this%20wholesome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharmistha%E2%80%99s%20disclaimer%20in%20the%20foreword%20that%20she%20is%20not%20a%20writer%20comes%20across%20as%20rhetorical%20humility.%20She%20does%20a%20deft%20job%20of%20chronicling%20what%20it%20was%20like%20being%20the%20daughter%20of%20Pranab%20Mukherjee%20(as%20advised%20by%20her%20friend%2C%20author%20Amitav%20Ghosh)%20while%20also%20etching%20a%20warm%2C%20loving%20picture%20of%20the%20human%20being%20behind%20the%20political%20persona%20of%20a%20workaholic%2C%20a%20leader%20whose%20political%20acumen%20was%20respected%20across%20the%20political%20divide%20(Bhutan%20king%20told%20his%20three%20wives%20that%20he%20was%20holding%20the%20umbrella%20for%20Sharmistha%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20her%20father%E2%80%9D)%20and%20across%20borders%20and%20yet%2C%20who%20managed%20to%20win%20a%20mere%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20his%20political%20life%20of%2048%20years%20(he%20first%20entered%20parliament%20as%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20in%201969).%20Through%20all%20of%20this%2C%20the%20backdrop%20of%20contemporary%20politics%20is%20never%20allowed%20to%20fade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20touches%20upon%20his%20own%20internal%20turmoils%20%E2%80%93%20how%20he%20struggled%20to%20keep%20his%20temper%20and%20chastised%20himself%20in%20the%20pages%20of%20his%20diary%20for%20failing%20to%20do%20so%20and%20his%20propensity%20to%20use%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%9Cfirmly%20and%20frankly%E2%80%9D%20to%20describe%20his%20own%20interventions%20while%20documenting%20many%20of%20his%20political%20meetings.%20She%20also%20shared%20witty%20yet%20politically%20loaded%20anecdotes%20of%20how%20the%20political%20blended%20into%20the%20personal%20(Pranab%20parrying%20his%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20query%20about%20why%20he%20won%E2%80%99t%20share%20his%20prime%20ministerial%20ambitions%20with%20Congress%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20with%20a%20hilarious%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20like%20you%20that%20I%20would%20throw%20a%20tantrum%20when%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20what%20I%20want%E2%80%9D).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20a%20no-nonsense%20but%20loving%20father%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20mould%20of%20many%20middle-class%20fathers%20of%20his%20generation.%20For%20example%20when%20ex-UK%20PM%20Margaret%20Thatcher%20met%20her%20during%20a%20visit%20to%20India%20and%20asked%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20the%20beauty%20and%20grace%20of%20a%20dancer.%20Are%20you%20a%20dancer%3F%E2%80%9D%20sending%20a%20young%20Sharmistha%20over%20the%20moon%2C%20Pranab%20gives%20his%20daughter%20a%20reality%20check%20that%20visiting%20dignitaries%20are%20briefed%20about%20family%20members%20of%20key%20people%20in%20the%20host%20country.%20But%20when%20Sharmistha%E2%80%99s%20performance%20in%20Rashtrapati%20Bhawan%20he%20objected%20to%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20she%20is%20not%20in%20the%20league%20of%20performers%20that%20normally%20get%20to%20be%20on%20that%20exalted%20stage%20goes%20off%20flawlessly%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20newly%20sworn-in%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%20Narendra%20Modi%20who%20Sharmistha%20had%20invited%20almost%20on%20an%20impulse%20much%20to%20the%20discomfiture%20of%20her%20father%2C%20the%20proud%20father%20records%20it%20in%20his%20precious%20diary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20has%20been%20made%20of%20Pranab%E2%80%99s%20observations%20about%20a%20younger%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20his%20diaries%2C%20coloured%20no%20doubt%20also%20by%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20book%E2%80%99s%20release%20%E2%80%93%20less%20than%20six%20months%20to%20the%20next%20parliamentary%20elections.%20Sharmistha%20launched%20a%20spirited%20counterattack%20to%20the%20Congress%20ecosystem%20at%20the%20launch%20event%20when%20she%20asked%20whether%20the%20proponents%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%20want%20to%20control%20what%20a%20man%20writes%20in%20his%20diary%20and%20what%20his%20daughter%20reminisces%20about%20him.%C2%A0%20Those%20diaries%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20book%20%E2%80%93%20also%20have%20countless%20instances%20of%20the%20trust%20deficit%20between%20Pranab%20and%20the%20Gandhis%20post-Indira%2C%20sometimes%20trying%20to%20address%20their%20genesis%20and%20at%20others%20offering%20Pranab%E2%80%99s%20own%20assessment%20like%20when%20he%20says%20of%20Sonia%3A%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20only%20trying%20to%20protect%20her%20own%20and%20her%20family%E2%80%99s%20interests.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20launch%20at%20the%20India%20International%20Centre%20on%20Monday%20was%20significantly%20bereft%20of%20any%20Congress%20leaders%20except%20former%20Union%20minister%20P.%20Chidambaram%2C%20whose%20coming%20was%20a%20surprise%20even%20for%20the%20author%20and%20who%2C%20ironically%20is%20also%20the%20man%20often%20accused%20by%20political%20opponents%20of%20having%20bugged%20Pranab%E2%80%99s%20office%20when%20both%20were%20a%20part%20of%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20cabinet.%20But%20there%20are%20unsavoury%20comments%20%E2%80%93%20admittedly%20far%20less%20scathing%20%E2%80%93%20made%20against%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20political%20divide%20in%20the%20book%20while%20tackling%20some%20of%20the%20criticism%20that%20had%20dogged%20Pranab%E2%80%99s%20public%20life%20(retrospective%20tax%2C%20constitutional%20crises%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20former%20president%E2%80%99s%20appearance%20on%20a%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20stage%20during%20the%20launch%20conversation%20with%20former%20diplomat%20Pawan%20Verma%2C%20the%20author%20could%20barely%20hide%20her%20glee%20about%20a%20tweet%20that%20she%20had%20come%20across%20during%20Pranab%E2%80%99s%20speech%20in%20which%20he%20had%20espoused%20the%20Congress%20ideology%20from%20a%20stage%20that%20is%20usually%20witness%20to%20professions%20of%20a%20different%20nature.%20%E2%80%9CPranab%20Mukherjee%20is%20trolling%20the%20RSS%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharmistha%20said%20while%20breaking%20into%20laughter.%20Pranab%E2%80%99s%20own%20justification%20about%20the%20criticism%20that%20his%20appearance%20gave%20%E2%80%9Clegitimacy%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20RSS%20was%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwho%20am%20I%20to%20give%20legitimacy%20to%20the%20RSS!%20The%20people%20of%20India%20have%20given%20legitimacy%20to%20the%20RSS%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20there%20is%20one%20thought%20one%20comes%20out%20with%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20clear%20intent%20that%20Pranab%20seems%20to%20have%20conveyed%20%E2%80%93%20that%20he%20hopes%20his%20dear%20%E2%80%9CMunni%E2%80%9D%20will%20one%20day%20write%20a%20book%20from%20the%20contents%20of%20his%20diary.%20Is%20Pranab%20Mukherjee%20trolling%20the%20Gandhis%20from%20beyond%20the%20grave%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAbantika%20Ghosh%20is%20a%20journalist%20and%20public%20policy%20professional.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702470704000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F31203418%2Fpranab-mukherjee.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fpranab-mukherjee-the-best-prime-minister-india-never-had%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sharmistha%20Mukherjee's%20book%20'Pranab%2C%20My%20Father%3A%20A%20Daughter%20Remembers'%20brings%20to%20the%20fore%20observations%20and%20apprehensions%20recorded%20in%20the%20former%20president's%20personal%20diary%2C%20which%20were%20never%20made%20public%20during%20his%20lifetime.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fpranab-mukherjee-the-best-prime-minister-india-never-had%2