3A%2F%2Fwww.zeebiz.com%2Findia%2Fnews-bihar-oath-ceremony-nitish-kumar-13-ministers-including-tarkishore-prasad-renu-devi-to-be-sworn-in-on-monday-140463%5C%22%3Eopted%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20lesser-known%20figures%20in%20the%20cabinet%20such%20as%20Tarkishore%20Prasad%20and%20Renu%20Kushwaha.%20Similarly%2C%20this%20time%2C%20the%20party%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-mohan-yadav-5-facts-about-new-madhya-pradesh-chief-minister-4664876%5C%22%3Echose%3C%2Fa%3E%20Mohan%20Yadav%20to%20become%20chief%20minister%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20first-time%20MLA%20Bhajanlal%20Sharma%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESushil%20Kumar%20Modi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESushil%20Kumar%20Modi%2C%20who%20had%20served%20as%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20since%20Nitish%20Kumar%20became%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20replacing%20Rabri%20Devi%20in%202005%2C%20performed%20reasonably%20well%20as%20both%20the%20finance%20minister%20and%20the%20party%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20he%20campaigned%20in%20Bihar%20in%20a%20manner%20similar%20to%20how%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20had%20campaigned%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESushil%20Modi%20was%20a%20prominent%20leader%20in%20the%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan-led%20Total%20Revolution%20in%201974%20and%20had%20risen%20significantly%20in%20politics%20through%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20(ABVP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20his%20supporters%20were%20optimistic%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20would%20%E2%80%9Caccommodate%E2%80%9D%20him%20in%20his%20cabinet%2C%20given%20his%20experience%2C%20pedigree%2C%20and%20loyalty%20to%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%E2%80%99s%20worldview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20party%20high%20command%20did%20just%20the%20opposite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Modi-Shah%20duo%20after%20the%202014%20general%20elections%2C%20not%20only%20removed%20him%20from%20the%20position%20of%20deputy%20CM%20but%20also%20relegated%20him%20to%20insignificance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20months%20after%20his%20removal%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Ckey%E2%80%9D%20BJP%20leader%2C%20he%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20He%20has%20a%20peripheral%20role%20to%20play%20in%20the%20party%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Chouhan%20%E2%80%93%20a%20five-time%20MP%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbhopal%2F5-time-mp-4-term-cm-what-next-for-shivraj-singh-chouhan%2Farticleshow%2F105916787.cms%5C%22%3Elongest-serving%20chief%20minister%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%93%20has%20been%20replaced%20by%20Mohan%20Yadav%2C%20a%20lesser-known%20party%20MLA%20from%20Ujjain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChouhan%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20increase%20the%20stipend%20from%20Rs%201%2C500%20to%20Rs%203%2C000%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98Ladli%20Behna%E2%80%99%20scheme%2C%20coupled%20with%20his%20intense%20campaigning%2C%20was%20believed%20to%20have%20provided%20traction%20to%20his%20party%20against%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20Chouhan%20meet%20the%20same%20fate%20as%20Sushil%20Modi%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20noteworthy%20that%20Sushil%20Modi%20enjoys%20the%20unique%20distinction%20of%20never%20losing%20an%20election%2C%20whether%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20or%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%2C%20ever%20since%20he%20made%20his%20debut%20in%20electoral%20politics%20in%201995.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20events%20unfolding%20from%20now%20on%20can%20only%20provide%20an%20answer%20to%20this%20question%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cera%20of%20surprises%E2%80%9D%20ushered%20in%20by%20the%20Modi-Shah%20duo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20thrown%20similar%20surprises%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20which%20were%20among%20the%20five%20states%20undergoing%20assembly%20elections%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20%E2%80%9Castonished%E2%80%9D%20its%20supporters%20and%20opponents%20by%20nominating%20the%20first-time%20MLA%20from%20Sanganer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-bjp-bhajanlal-sharma%5C%22%3EBhajan%20Lal%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20the%20Rajasthan%20chief%20minister.%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20too%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-bjp-ends-week-long-suspense-names-vishnu-deo-sai-as-next-chief-minister%5C%22%3EVishnu%20Deo%20Sai%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20tribal%20community%20and%20relatively%20junior%20among%20the%20party%20veterans%20as%20its%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20all%20these%20%E2%80%9Csidelined%E2%80%9D%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20Chouhan%2C%20Sushil%20Modi%2C%20Raje%2C%20and%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20are%20much%20younger%20than%20the%2075%20years%20of%20age%20that%20the%20Modi-Shah%20brand%20of%20the%20BJP%20has%20set%20for%20%E2%80%98retiring%E2%80%99%20from%20politics%20and%20joining%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Fopinion%2Fcolumnists%2F030423%2Fsunil-gatade-has-entire-bjp-become-a-margdarshak-mandal.html%5C%22%3EMargdarshak%20Mandal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20fact%2C%20they%20are%20much%20younger%20than%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20was%20born%20on%20September%2017%2C%201950%2C%20according%20to%20his%20certificates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20political%20strategy%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20like%20Chouhan%20and%20Sushil%20Modi%2C%20who%20rose%20to%20prominence%20during%20the%20era%20of%20A.B.%20Vajpayee%20and%20L.K.%20Advani%2C%20were%20significant%20figures%20in%20the%20BJP%20in%20their%20respective%20states%20before%20Narendra%20Modi%20became%20prime%20minister%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20arises%20whether%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20is%20deliberately%20sidelining%20these%20experienced%20leaders%20for%20a%20generational%20change%2C%20to%20introduce%20new%20faces%20and%20promote%20freshness%20within%20the%20party.%20Is%20this%20a%20strategy%20to%20counter%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhow-nitish-kumar-is-keeping-the-issue-of-bihar-caste-survey-alive%5C%22%3Ecaste-based%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20implementation%20of%2065%25%20reservation%20for%20backward%20classes%20in%20government%20jobs%2C%20a%20move%20embraced%20by%20parties%20within%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20as%20a%20counter%20to%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20politics%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Gorakhpur-based%20senior%20RSS-BJP%20leader%20and%20staunch%20loyalist%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20Yogi%20told%20this%20writer%2C%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20%E2%80%9CNarendra%20Modi%20is%20systematically%20sidelining%20all%20the%20senior%20and%20strong%20leaders%20with%20the%20sole%20purpose%20to%20return%20to%20power%20in%202024.%20He%20feels%20threatened%20by%20the%20leaders%20of%20superior%20pedigree%20and%20has%20been%20working%20in%20a%20ruthless%20manner%20to%20remove%20the%20%E2%80%98obstacles%E2%80%99%20from%20his%20way%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%202024%20polls.%20And%2C%20he%20has%20got%20Amit%20Shah%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98best%20hatchet%20man%E2%80%99%20to%20do%20the%20job%20for%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Modi-Shah%20duo%20has%20captured%20the%20party%20and%20the%20RSS%2C%20too.%20Modi%20and%20Shah%20have%20grown%20in%20power%20but%20the%20BJP%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20democratic%20party%20that%20it%20used%20to%20be%20during%20the%20Vajpayee-Advani%20era%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20observation%20made%20by%20the%20person%20cited%20above%20echoes%20the%20sentiments%20of%20supporters%20of%20Adityanath%2C%20who%20has%20established%20his%20own%20network%20of%20followers%20drawn%20from%20his%20Hindu%20Vahini%2C%20for