mp%3BK%20by%20September%2030%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20verdict%20came%20as%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20set%20to%20complete%20five%20years%20under%20Central%20rule%20on%20December%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20has%20repeatedly%20refused%20to%20conduct%20assembly%20elections%2C%20citing%20security%20issues%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20among%20other%20reasons%2C%20even%20as%20the%20poll%20body%20is%20preparing%20to%20hold%20the%20parliamentary%20elections%20in%20the%20union%20territory%20(UT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20ECI%20will%20revive%20the%20democratic%20process%2C%20which%20has%20been%20put%20on%20a%20back%20burner%20since%202018%2C%20and%20allow%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20to%20exercise%20their%20democratic%20right%2C%20remains%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20speculation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20certain%20is%20that%20the%20saffron%20party%20would%20like%20to%20come%20to%20power%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20only%20Muslim-majority%20region%20on%20its%20own%2C%20ideally%20with%20a%20Hindu%20chief%20minister%2C%20after%20getting%20judicial%20approval%20for%20its%20%E2%80%98big%20move%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Noor%20A.%20Baba%2C%20former%20dean%20of%20social%20sciences%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Kashmir%2C%20believes%20that%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20has%20%E2%80%9Cpolitically%20engineered%E2%80%9D%20J%26amp%3BK%20after%20downgrading%20it%20into%20a%20union%20territory%20which%20could%20influence%20the%20outcome%20of%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Reorganisation%20Act%2C%202019%20became%20a%20law%2C%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20redrew%20the%20electoral%20landscape%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20When%20the%20controversial%20delimitation%20exercise%20was%20over%2C%20Jammu%2C%20a%20BJP%20stronghold%2C%20woke%20up%20with%20six%20additional%20assembly%20seats%20in%20its%20kitty%20while%20Kashmir%20got%20just%20one%20extra%20seat%2C%20despite%20a%20clear%20demographic%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDelimitation%20has%20completely%20changed%20the%20electoral%20arithmetic%20and%20tilted%20the%20balance%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP.%20Even%20some%20electoral%20boundaries%20have%20been%20carved%20to%20ensure%20Hindu%20majority%20in%20some%20constituencies%20of%20Rajouri%2C%20Reasi%20and%20Chenab%20valley%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jammu-based%20author%20and%20editor%20Anuradha%20Bhasin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ends%20Matter%2C%20Not%20the%20Means%3A%20Decoding%20SC's%20Approval%20for%20Reading%20Down%20of%20Article%20370%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fends-matter-not-the-means-decoding-scs-approval-for-reading-down-of-article-370%5C%22%3EEnds%20Matter%2C%20Not%20the%20Means%3A%20Decoding%20SC%E2%80%99s%20Approval%20for%20Reading%20Down%20of%20Article%20370%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20saffron%20party%20is%20also%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20Gujjars%2C%20Bakkerwals%20and%20Paharis%20by%20raising%20the%20bogey%20of%20%E2%80%98empowering%20the%20marginalised%E2%80%99%20with%20a%20new%20reservation%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20delivered%20its%20verdict%20on%20Article%20370%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20gave%20its%20nod%20to%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Reorganisation%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%20which%20increases%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Legislative%20Assembly%20from%2083%20to%2090%20of%20which%20seven%20seats%20are%20reserved%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%2C%20in%20a%20first%2C%20nine%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20also%20empowers%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20to%20nominate%20two%20members%20from%20the%20Kashmiri%20migrant%20community%20and%20one%20from%20Displaced%20Persons%20from%20Pakistan-occupied%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20to%20the%20Legislative%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaba%20said%20that%20given%20India%E2%80%99s%20federal%20structure%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20should%20have%20left%20these%20landmark%20changes%20for%20a%20democratic%20dispensation%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20to%20undertake%2C%20asserting%20that%20in%20the%20process%20%E2%80%9CKashmir%20has%20been%20marginalised%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20has%20been%20manoeuvred%20in%20a%20manner%20which%20has%20reduced%20the%20majority%20into%20a%20minority%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20changes%20effected%20by%20the%20delimitation%20and%20assembly%20reservation%20might%20help%20the%20BJP%20to%20cross%20the%20mark%20of%2025%20seats%20it%20had%20won%20in%202014%20assembly%20elections%2C%20even%20its%20most%20fervent%20supporters%20know%20that%20the%20party%20can%E2%80%99t%20come%20close%20to%20magic%20number%20of%2046%20required%20to%20form%20the%20government%20in%20the%20new%2C%2090-member%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20effect%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20mollycoddling%20with%20like-minded%20leaders%20and%20Kashmir-centric%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202019%2C%20two%20new%20formations%20have%20also%20sprouted%20on%20the%20political%20horizon%20which%20are%20led%20by%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20chief%20minister%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20and%20former%20leader%20of%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%E2%80%99s%20PDP%2C%20Altaf%20Bukhari%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20have%20made%20public%20displays%20of%20affection%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20National%20Conference%20(NC)%20and%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%2C%20who%20are%20part%20of%20the%20fledgling%20Gupkar%20alliance%2C%20have%20vowed%20to%20fight%20the%20BJP%20and%20restore%20Article%20370.%20But%20the%20two%20are%20also%20facing%20perhaps%20the%20most%20difficult%20times%20in%20their%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Rekha%20Chaudhary%2C%20a%20Jammu-based%20academic%20and%20political%20analyst%2C%20believes%20that%20the%20next%20assembly%20election%20will%20be%20a%20direct%20contest%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20National%20Conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Kashmir%2C%20it%20is%20the%20NC%20which%20is%20quite%20confident%20of%20doing%20well.%20Not%20only%20because%20it%20showed%20its%20strength%20during%20the%20DDC%20elections%20held%20couple%20of%20years%20earlier%20but%20also%20because%20the%20PDP%20has%20been%20crisis-ridden%20with%20senior%20leaders%20leaving%20it%20over%20the%20period.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9COther%20parties%2C%20including%20Sajad%20Lone%E2%80%99s%20Peoples%20Conference%2C%20have%20a%20limited%20influence%20and%20they%20may%20well%20end%20up%20on%20the%20other%20side%20after%20the%20elections%20results%20are%20out.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20political%20analyst%20and%20editor%20Zafar%20Choudhary%20believes%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20verdict%20has%20brought%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfundamental%20change%E2%80%9D%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20political%20environment%20and%20the%20situation%20might%20%E2%80%9Cget%20difficult%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20local%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Kashmir%2C%20BJP%20has%20allies%20in%20a%20political%20environment%20where%20no%20party%20can%20get%20any%20serious%20listeners%20to%20the%20claims%20of%20being%20pro-special%20status.%20This%20%E2%80%98level%20playing%20field%E2%80%99%20opens%20space%20for%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20local%20allies%2C%E2%80%9D%20Choudhary%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Gupkar%20alliance%20getting%20sucked%20into%20petty%20political%20tirades%2C%20political%20analysts%20believe%20J%26amp%3BK%20assembly%20elections%20could%20well%20turn%20into%20an%20exercise%20in%20vanity%20with%20a%20pie%20of%20power%20hanging%20for%20anyone%20willing%20to%20share%20the%20spoils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Jammu%2C%20which%20helped%20the%20BJP%20more%20than%20double%20its%20tally%20in%20the%202014%20assembly%20election%2C%20might%20not%20be%20a%20cakewalk%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20Jammu%20region%2C%20though%20the%20BJP%20is%20facing%20multiple%20challenges%2C%20it%20is%20also%20comfortable%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20is%20no%20alternative%20to%20it.%20The%20Congress%2C%20the%20only%20party%20that%20could%20have%20challenged%20it%2C%20has%20been%20weakened%20after%20Azad%E2%80%99s%20exit%20and%20his%20party%20has%20not%20really%20taken%20off.%20NC%20has%20almost%20withdrawn%20from%20the%20region%20and%20is%20mainly%20focusing%20on%20Kashmir%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chaudhary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20exit%20of%20Devendra%20Rana%20and%20S.S.%20Slathia%2C%20the%20NC%E2%80%99s%20most%20visible%20Jammu%20faces%20who%20have%20since%20switched%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20party%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20active%20in%20the%20plains%20of%20Jammu.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20this%20leaves%20the%20field%20open%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chaudhary%2C%20who%20taught%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Jammu%2C%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Kashmir%2C%20analysts%20believe%20that%20the%20election%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20no-holds-barred%20contest%20where%20the%20traditional%20parties%20like%20NC%20and%20PDP%20will%20struggle%20and%20bleed%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20multi-pronged%20assault%20which%20has%20sent%20dozens%20of%20their%20leaders%20flocking%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98right%E2%80%99%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20exception%20of%20the%20PDP%20which%20has%20not%20changed%20much%20of%20its%20basic%20orientation%2C%20other%20parties%20have%20almost%20moved%20on.%20The%20NC%2C%20mainly%20because%20of%20the%20future%20that%20it%20sees%20for%20itself%20in%20the%20coming%20elections%2C%20has%20adopted%20a%20more%20pragmatic%20approach.%20Much%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20decision%2C%20it%20had%20delinked%20its%20politics%20from%20the%20issue%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20stating%20that%20this%20was%20a%20%E2%80%98legal%20issue%E2%80%99%20pending%20with%20the%20court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalyst%20Choudhary%20said%20that%20any%20party%20or%20alliance%20will%20have%20to%20win%2048%20seats%2C%20three%20more%20than%20the%20halfway%20mark%20of%2045%20seats%2C%20to%20form%20the%20next%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20will%20need%20only%2043%20seats%20as%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20is%20empowered%20to%20nominate%20three%20members.%20Given%20the%20voting%20pattern%20of%20the%20last%20three%20assembly%20elections%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20for%20any%20alliance%20to%20clinch%20the%20magic%20number%20of%2048%2C%E2%80%9D%20Choudhary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20case%20of%20a%20close%20contest%2C%20three%20officially%20nominated%20members%20could%20hold%20the%20key%20to%20the%20government%20formation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaba%20said%20that%20the%20structural%20changes%20that%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20might%20be%20difficult%20to%20undo%20once%20democracy%20and%20statehood%20is%20restored%3A%20%E2%80%9CThey%20may%20or%20may%20not%20work%20for%20the%20BJP%20but%20even%20if%20the%20party%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20come%20to%20power%2C%20some%20of%20the%20policies%20will%20have%20to%20continue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhatever%20is%20happening%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20is%20happening%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20Centre%20is%20behaving%20as%20per%20the%20political%20calculations%20of%20the%20BJP.%20Undoing%20of%20Article%20370%20had%20a%20political%20objective%20and%20these%20changes%20fall%20into%20that%20pattern.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702459854000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13140041%2F16147040338_e14a11ca31_o.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-will-the-supreme-courts-article-370-judgment-mean-for-politics-in-jk%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20directed%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20to%20conduct%20assembly%20polls%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20by%20September%2030%2C%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-will-the-supreme-courts-article-370-judgment-mean-for-politics-in-jk%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Does%20the%20COP28%20deal%20mean%20the%201.5C%20of%20warming%20target%20is%20still%20possible%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702459020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F70x70%2Fskynews-sultan-al-jaber-cop28_6392094.jpg%3F20231213163207%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fcop28-was-historic-but-the-test-will-be-whether-it-keeps-global-warming-to-15c-13029342%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20lot%20of%20what%20happens%20at%20a%20United%20Nations%20climate%20summit%20is%20just%20hot%20air%3A%20voluntary%20pledges%2C%20non-binding%20agreements%2C%20PR%20opportunities%20and%20showboating%20from%20those%20who%20want%20to%20talk%20the%20talk%20but%20not%20walk%20the%20walk.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fcop28-was-historic-but-the-test-will-be-whether-it-keeps-global-warming-to-1-5c-13029342%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fcop28-was-historic-but-the-test-will-be-whether-it-keeps-global-warming-to-1-5c-13029342%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fcop28-was-historic-but-the-test-will-be-whether-it-keeps-global-warming-to-1-5c-13029342%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prasanth%20Vijay's%20Film%20'Daayam'%20Unravels%20Kerala's%20Gender%20Paradox%20Amidst%20Grief%20and%20Patriarchy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13131921%2Fimage-1601.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EPrasanth%20Vijay%E2%80%99s%20movie%20%3Cem%3EDaayam%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%E2%80%98Inheritance%E2%80%99)%2C%20which%20is%20being%20screened%20at%20the%20ongoing%2028th%20International%20Film%20Festival%20of%20Kerala%2C%20is%20about%20a%20teenage%20girl%20learning%20to%20cope%20with%20the%20loss%20of%20her%20mother.%20Her%20home%2C%20that%20of%20a%20typical%20upper%20middle-class%20nuclear%20family%2C%20is%20largely%20where%20the%20story%20takes%20place.%20But%20the%20film%20throws%20up%20some%20keen%20observations%20about%20the%20larger%20Malayali%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrasanth%20says%20that%20the%20film%20was%20planned%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20to%20be%20shot%20in%20the%20confines%20of%20a%20domestic%20space.%20He%20roped%20in%20filmmaker%20Indu%20Lakshmi%20%E2%80%93%20they%20both%20used%20to%20work%20for%20Infosys%20%E2%80%93%20to%20write%20the%20script%20and%20finish%20the%20shoot%20in%20a%20month.%20However%2C%20the%20making%20of%20the%20film%20got%20delayed.%20It%20was%20finally%20finished%20when%20he%20was%20already%20busy%20with%20his%20third%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDaayam%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20selected%20in%20the%20National%20Film%20Development%20Corporation%E2%80%99s%20Film%20Bazaar%20Recommends%202022.%20It%20had%20its%20world%20premiere%20at%20the%20MAMI%20Mumbai%20Film%20Festival%202023.%20It%20has%20also%20been%20selected%20for%20the%20Chicago%20International%20Children%E2%80%99s%20Film%20Festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20immediate%20locus%20of%20the%20film%20is%20the%20famous%20Malayalam%20short%20story%20by%20Madhavikkutty%20aka%20Kamala%20Das%2C%20titled%20%3Cem%3ENeypaayasam%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%E2%80%98Ghee%20Kheer%E2%80%99).%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20heart-wrenching%20account%20of%20the%20sudden%20death%20of%20a%20woman%20and%20the%20sweet%20dish%20she%20leaves%20behind%20being%20relished%20by%20her%20unsuspecting%20young%20children%2C%20with%20the%20devastated%20father%20looking%20on.%20A%20powerful%20motif%20for%20the%20Malayali%20literary%20public.%20But%20there%20is%20yet%20another%20story%20that%20is%20closer%20to%20%3Cem%3EDaayam%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20inner%20trajectory%3A%20Ashitha%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EAmma%20Ennodu%20Paranja%20Nunakal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(%E2%80%98The%20Lies%20Mother%20Told%20Me%E2%80%99).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20has%20a%20%3Cem%3ENeypaayasam%3C%2Fem%3E%20moment%20when%20Kalyani%20suddenly%20loses%20her%20mother%2C%20Renuka%2C%20to%20cerebral%20haemorrhage%2C%20and%20her%20recipe%20book%20is%20discovered%20from%20a%20kitchen%20shelf.%20The%20relatives%20wax%20eloquent%20about%20Renuka%E2%80%99s%20Neypaayasam%2C%20but%20its%20recipe%20is%20missing%20from%20the%20book.%20The%20movie%20has%20a%20deliberately%20slow%20pace%2C%20set%20to%20soulful%20music%20by%20Varkey%2C%20letting%20the%20shocking%20fact%20of%20the%20death%20sink%20in%20both%20for%20the%20individuals%20on%20screen%20and%20the%20audience%20watching%20them.%20But%20%3Cem%3EDaayam%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20not%20only%20about%20grief%20after%20profound%20loss%2C%20but%20a%20fly-on-the%20wall%20narrative%20of%20its%20aftermath%2C%20with%20elements%20of%20intrigue%20and%20drama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20death%20of%20the%20woman%20and%20the%20exit%20of%20the%20extended%20family%20after%20the%20customary%20few%20days%2C%20the%20house%20falls%20into%20a%20disarray.%20Unwashed%20laundry%20and%20kitchen%20disasters%20rule%20the%20day%2C%20but%20Kalyani%20and%20her%20father%20find%20their%20rhythm%20in%20time%20(stellar%20performances%20by%20Aathira%20Rajeev%20and%20Pradeep%20Geedha).%20Yet%2C%20things%20go%20horribly%20wrong%20and%20Kalyani%20is%20ultimately%20forced%20to%20become%20the%20adult%20of%20the%20family%20almost%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13133358%2Fimage-1602.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221122%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13133358%2Fimage-1602.png%201122w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13133358%2Fimage-1602-300x193.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13133358%2Fimage-1602-1024x659.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689006%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22722%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20the%20movie%20%E2%80%98Daayam%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrasanth%E2%80%99s%202017%20debut%20movie%2C%20%3Cem%3EAthisayangalude%20Venal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%E2%80%98Summer%20of%20Miracles%E2%80%99)%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20also%20about%20losing%20a%20parent.%20The%20protagonist%2C%20a%20young%20boy%2C%20struggles%20to%20cope%20with%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20disappearance%20and%20Prasanth%20agrees%20that%20%3Cem%3EDaayam%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cspiritual%20sequel%20to%20my%20first%20work%E2%80%9D.%20One%20might%20add%20that%20Kalyani%2C%20too%2C%20faces%20the%20disappearance%20of%20her%20father%2C%20all%20but%20physically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20an%20understated%20tale%20of%20aching%2C%20the%20film%20gradually%20grows%20into%20a%20not-so-subtle%20study%20of%20patriarchy.%20While%20some%20of%20the%20plot-points%20feel%20forced%20and%20with%20the%20climax%20bordering%20on%20the%20regressive%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20but%20an%20unfortunately%20accurate%20narrative%20of%20a%20Kerala%20entrenched%20in%20superstitions%2C%20casteism%2C%20and%20elitism%3B%20its%20convenient%20veneer%20of%20progressiveness%20ably%20concealing%20the%20rot%20inside.%20%3Cem%3EDaayam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20effect%2C%20is%20a%20provocative%20portrayal%20of%20the%20gender%20paradox%20of%20Kerala.%20Though%20the%20state%20consistently%20tops%20social%20indices%2C%20its%20homes%20reek%20of%20men%E2%80%99s%20entitlement.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cds.ac.in%2Fkrpcds%2Fpublication%2Fdownloads%2Fw42.pdf%5C%22%3Enational%20sample%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kerala%20ranks%20at%20the%20bottom%20among%20the%20larger%20states%20in%20South%20India%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20proportion%20of%20women%20in%20the%20overall%20workforce.%20This%2C%20despite%20having%20a%20larger%20share%20of%20enrolment%20in%20higher%20education%20than%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarriage%20and%20domestic%20responsibilities%20are%20still%20considered%20the%20ultimate%20virtue%20for%20women%20across%20classes%20which%20cost%20them%20their%20dreams%20and%20career%20plans%2C%20a%20fact%20backed%20by%20the%20Kerala%20Knowledge%20Economy%20Mission%20survey.%20%3Cem%3EDaayam%3C%2Fem%3E%20holds%20a%20mirror%20to%20this%20reality%20when%20Renuka%2C%20a%20teacher%2C%20dies%20and%20nobody%20talks%20about%20her%20profession%20but%20only%20about%20her%20cooking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20a%20female%20writer%20has%20helped%20the%20film%20in%20gaining%20perspectives%20that%20I%20would%20not%20have%20been%20able%20to%20explore%20otherwise%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prasanth.%20The%20unglamorous%20and%20unflattering%20aspects%20of%20homemaking%20are%20indeed%20shown%20with%20precision.%20In%20a%20house%20reverberating%20with%20Malayalam%20poetry%20from%20across%20ages%20and%20happy-family%20vibes%2C%20there%20are%20hints%20of%20a%20woman%2C%20Renuka%2C%20leading%20the%20life%20of%20a%20volcano%2C%20with%20sporadic%20releases%20of%20fire%20and%20ash%2C%20fated%20to%20eventually%20explode%20and%20die.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20she%20treads%20the%20age-old%20paths%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9Cchildren%E2%80%99s%20room%20to%20the%20husband%E2%80%99s%20bedroom%20to%20the%20kitchen%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20recounted%20by%20Ashitha%20in%20her%20short%20story%2C%20which%20ends%20with%20the%20daughter%20realising%20that%20her%20mother%20was%20lying%20all%20along%20about%20the%20simple%20recipe%20for%20marital%20bliss.%20But%20by%20then%2C%20she%20had%20already%20learned%20the%20language%20of%20silence%2C%20like%20the%20umpteen%20women%20before%20her.%20In%20a%20striking%20continuity%2C%20Kalyani%20is%20seen%20silently%20inheriting%20(hence%20%3Cem%3EDaayam%3C%2Fem%3E)%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20kitchen%20and%20her%20recipe%20book%2C%20oddly%20evoking%20memories%20of%20the%202021%20film%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EGreat%20Indian%20Kitchen%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20had%20the%20lead%20woman%20storm%20out%20of%20the%20kitchen%2C%20showing%20domestic%20drudgery%20for%20what%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20unlike%20such%20movies%2C%20Prasanth%20says%20his%20films%20are%20not%20looking%20to%20serve%20justice%20or%20provide%20closure%20to%20its%20protagonists.%20%E2%80%9CMuch%20has%20been%20left%20unsaid%2C%20expecting%20the%20viewers%20to%20fill%20in%20even%20as%20they%20walk%20out%20of%20the%20cinema%20and%20long%20after%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECuriously%20enough%2C%20the%20filmmaker%20feels%20that%20the%20viewers%20outside%20Kerala%20did%20not%20read%20too%20much%20into%20the%20climax%3A%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20able%20to%20relate%20to%20Kalyani%E2%80%99s%20affinity%20to%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20kitchen%2C%20a%20safe%20space%20of%20happy%20memories.%20But%20many%20Malayali%20viewers%20living%20in%20Kerala%20complained%20about%20the%20%E2%80%98meek%E2%80%99%20ending.%20What%20I%20have%20to%20tell%20them%20is%2C%20Kalyani%20is%20only%20holding%20onto%20whatever%20she%20can%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20teenager%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20her%20world%20that%20got%20suddenly%20upended.%20The%20rest%20is%20for%20the%20viewer%20to%20interpret.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20one%20hopes%20Kalyani%20gets%20the%20recipe%20right%20as%20she%20attempts%20to%20cook%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20Neypaayasam%20using%20a%20non-existent%20recipe.%20And%20power%20to%20break%20an%20inheritance%20of%20silence%20that%20could%20very%20well%20have%20killed%20her%20mother.%20%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702458007000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13131921%2Fimage-1601.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fprasanth-vijays-film-daayam-unravels-keralas-gender-paradox-amidst-grief-and-patriarchy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20film's%20immediate%20focus%20is%20Kamala%20Das's%20famous%20Malayalam%20short%20story%2C%20'Neypaayasam'.%20It's%20a%20heart-wrenching%20account%20of%20the%20sudden%20death%20of%20a%20woman%20and%20the%20sweet%20dish%20she%20leaves%20behind%20being%20relished%20by%20her%20unsuspecting%20young%20children%2C%20with%20the%20devastated%20father%20looking%20on.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fprasanth-vijays-film-daayam-unravels-keralas-gender-paradox-amidst-grief-and-patriarchy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Constantly%20Conspiring'%3A%20Hemant%20Soren%20After%20ED%20Summons%20CM%20for%20Sixth%20Time%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13134050%2FGBKLVxBbkAA4bPJ.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20what%20can%20be%20perceived%20as%20a%20continued%20assault%20on%20opposition%20leaders%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20by%20using%20central%20agencies%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20had%20asked%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20to%20present%20himself%20for%20questioning%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20this%20past%20December%2012.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20most%20opposition%20leaders%20had%20adhered%20to%20such%20summons%20by%20the%20agency%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20Soren%2C%20the%20top%20leader%20of%20the%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20(JMM)%2C%20has%2C%20however%2C%20refused%20to%20be%20questioned%20by%20ED%20%E2%80%93%20even%20after%20five%20such%20summons%20had%20been%20issued%20to%20him%20in%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20news%20reports%2C%20the%20ED%20had%20issued%20him%20summons%20for%20the%20fifth%20time%20in%20the%20case%20early%20this%20week%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20present%20himself%20at%20its%20Ranchi%20office%20on%20December%2012.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EED%20had%20previously%20issued%20summons%20to%20Soren%20in%20the%20same%20case%20on%20August%2014%20and%2024%3B%20on%20September%209%20and%2023%3B%20and%20on%20October%204.%20However%2C%20Soren%20chose%20to%20go%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20protection%20from%20ED%20stating%20that%20the%20summons%20were%20%E2%80%9Cunwarranted%E2%80%9D.%20In%20his%20petition%2C%20he%20told%20the%20SC%20that%20ED%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20targeting%20political%20opposition%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20past%20September%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalheraldindia.com%2Fnational%2Fsc-asks-jharkhand-cm-soren-to-approach-hc-against-ed-summons%5C%22%3Easked%20him%20to%20petition%20the%20Jharkhand%20high%20court%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fed-targeting-political-opposition-jharkhand-cm-hemant-soren-urges-supreme-court-to-monitor-eds-functioning-lay-down-norms-237994%5C%22%3Echallenged%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20ED%20on%20the%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20high%20court%2C%20in%20October%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Franchi-news%2Fin-setback-to-hemant-soren-jharkhand-hc-dismisses-his-plea-against-ed-summons-101697184800885.html%5C%22%3Edismissed%20the%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20summons%20had%20already%20elapsed.%20Another%20contention%20of%20the%20court%20was%20that%20the%20issue%20of%20section%2050%20and%2063%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20that%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20petition%20had%20challenged%2C%20has%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Findia%2Fsupreme-court-to-examine-validity-of-two-pmla-provisions%2Farticleshow%2F99071914.cms%5C%22%3Ebeen%20dealt%20with%20by%20the%20SC%20in%20a%20separate%20case%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20second%20contention%2C%20the%20ED%20had%20issued%20a%20fresh%20summons%20to%20Soren.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20central%20agency%20has%20also%20carried%20out%20a%20few%20arrests%20in%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20October%2C%20hearing%20another%20case%2C%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20had%20stated%20that%20ED%20can%20issue%20summons%20to%20someone%20but%20that%20it%20does%20not%20have%20the%20power%20to%20arrest%20the%20person.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20morning%20of%20December%2012%2C%20a%20security%20cordon%20at%20the%20Ranchi%20office%20of%20the%20ED%20was%20put%20in%20place%20to%20await%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20arrival%20at%20around%2011%20am%2C%20ostensibly%20to%20have%20his%20statement%20recorded%20in%20the%20case%20involving%20a%20land%20deal.%20However%2C%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20cavalcade%20passed%20it%20to%20proceed%20to%20a%20pre-scheduled%20meeting%20in%20Dumka%20district%2C%20leading%20to%20some%20amount%20of%20confusion%20among%20waiting%20reporters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoon%20after%20the%20cavalcade%20passed%20by%20the%20ED%20office%2C%20an%20official%20from%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20delivered%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20regional%20office%2C%20the%20details%20of%20which%20have%20not%20been%20divulged%20either%20by%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20office%20or%20by%20the%20ED.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fjharkhand-chief-minister-skips-ed-summons-for-questioning-in-money-laundering-case%2Fcid%2F1986462%5C%22%3Eaddressing%20the%20crowd%20assembled%20at%20the%20district%E2%80%99s%20Koraiya%20panchayat%20area%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Soren%20accused%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20which%20is%20the%20principal%20opposition%20in%20the%20state%2C%20of%20conspiring%20against%20his%20government.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20people%20thought%20that%20I%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20attend%20the%20programme%20today.%20Our%20opposition%20has%20constantly%20been%20conspiring%20against%20the%20government%20and%20trying%20to%20divert%20people%E2%80%99s%20attention.%20We%20will%20not%20tolerate%20the%20people%20who%20defame%20this%20sacred%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20him%20as%20having%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReacting%20to%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20depose%20before%20the%20ED%2C%20the%20Jharkhand%20wing%20of%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20demanded%20stern%20action%20against%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20with%20its%20state%20spokesperson%20Pratul%20Shahdeo%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CED%20has%20given%20enough%20time%20to%20CM%2C%20now%20it%20should%20take%20strong%20action.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%20had%20issued%20summons%20to%20Soren%20in%20a%20mining%20case%20earlier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20August%202022%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20Soren%20asking%20him%20why%20he%20should%20not%20be%20disqualified%20for%20being%20named%20in%20that%20cash-for-profit%20mining%20case.%20The%20notice%20was%20in%20response%20to%20a%20memorandum%20submitted%20by%20state%20BJP.%20The%20BJP%20had%20then%20submitted%20the%20same%20memorandum%20to%20the%20state%20governor%2C%20raising%20speculations%20about%20possible%20dismissal%20of%20the%20JMM%20government%20in%20the%20state.%20However%2C%20the%20governor%2C%20after%20visits%20to%20Delhi%2C%20had%20decided%20not%20to%20go%20ahead%20on%20the%20matter.%20More%20details%20on%20the%20issue%20can%20be%20read%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fjharkhand-chief-minister-skips-ed-summons-for-questioning-in-money-laundering-case%2Fcid%2F1986462%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Soren%20government%20came%20to%20power%20in%20Jharkhand%20in%20December%202019%20after%20the%20BJP%20lost%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20polls.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702456241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13134050%2FGBKLVxBbkAA4bPJ.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fconstantly-conspiring-hemant-soren-after-ed-summons-cm-for-sixth-time%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ED%20had%20asked%20him%20to%20present%20himself%20at%20its%20Ranchi%20office%20on%20December%2012.%20Soren%20did%20not%20turn%20up%20and%20attended%20a%20Dumka%20function%20instead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fconstantly-conspiring-hemant-soren-after-ed-summons-cm-for-sixth-time%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Triumph%20of%20the%20Modi%20Model%20Rests%20on%20Three%20Key%20Weapons%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F12114331%2F33F81A3F-BCF6-4D05-975C-264958F029F4_1_105_c.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2Fp%2Fbjp-experiments-with-unknown-cm-2%5C%22%3Epiece%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20first%20published%20on%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%