A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fba36abeb-4bc4-464a-a972-05a4ba407c7a%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1702536247409000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw05eo_qZzHfIm08WtXe_-zz%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0future%20opposition%20meetings%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20had%20to%20put%20off%20its%20meeting%20scheduled%20for%20December%206.%20%E2%80%9CKnives%20are%20out%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20TV%20channels%20gleefully%20declared.%20The%20Congress%2C%20on%20its%20part%2C%20also%20contributed%20to%20the%20confusion%20by%20fixing%20the%20December%206%20meeting%20without%20consulting%20even%20senior%20allies%20like%20M.K.%20Stalin%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20does%20the%20triumph%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Chhatisgarh%20really%20ensure%20a%20BJP%20victory%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20as%20Modi%20claims%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20closer%20look%20at%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20results%20shows%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20already%20reached%20saturation%20point%20in%20all%20Hindi%20states.%20There%20is%20no%20room%20for%20further%20improvement%20as%20the%20BJP%20has%2025%20out%20of%2025%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%2028%20out%20of%2029%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20nine%20of%2011%20in%20Chhatisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20party%20bagged%20all%20seven%20seats%2C%20all%2010%20in%20Haryana%2C%20and%20all%2026%20in%20Gujarat.%20The%202019%20Balakot%20bravado%20had%20its%20impact%20on%20outlying%20states%20in%20the%20south%20and%20even%20in%20opposition%20strongholds%20like%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Bihar.%20The%20BJP%20cannot%20achieve%20these%20figures%20without%20precipitating%20a%20similar%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPsephologist%20Yogendra%20Yadav%20has%20also%20turned%20to%20vote%20shares%20to%20argue%20why%20Modi%E2%80%99s%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fce9a9974-e894-4220-bf77-801a2d362371%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fce9a9974-e894-4220-bf77-801a2d362371%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1702536247409000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0e5tfZuzghCFsRipbpUe6G%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%98hat%20trick%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20theory%20was%20flawed.%20The%20difference%20between%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20was%20less%20than%202%25%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%204%25%20in%20Chhatisgarh.%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20retained%20power%2C%20the%20difference%20was%20a%20respectable%208%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20explains%20this%20gulf%20between%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20votes%3F%20While%20there%20can%20be%20many%20factors%2C%20there%20are%20three%20which%20need%20highlighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20is%20setting%20in%20motion%20ED%2FCBI%2FIT%20raids%20not%20just%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20an%20election%20%E2%80%93%20which%20has%20been%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20practice%20%E2%80%93%20but%20even%20after%20the%20election%20process%20has%20begun.%20This%20marks%20the%20start%20of%20a%20dangerous%20new%20strategy.%20It%20amounts%20to%20intentionally%20disrupting%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20legitimate%20election%20work%20by%20way%20of%20choking%20the%20flow%20of%20funds%20and%20arbitrarily%20seizing%20campaign%20materials.%20All%20the%20while%20allowing%20the%20ruling%20party%20a%20free%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20ban%20by%20the%20EC%20on%20the%20introduction%20of%20new%20government%20largesse%20after%20elections%20have%20been%20announced.%20There%20is%20little%20chance%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20accepting%20the%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20a%20similar%20ban%20on%20ED%2FCBI%2FIncome%20tax%20assaults%20during%20the%20elections.%20Look%20at%20the%20way%20the%20ED%2FCBI%20hounded%20the%20opposition%20during%20the%20elections%20while%20treating%20BJP%20leaders%20with%20kid%20gloves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20disrupt%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20election%20work%2C%20the%20ED%2C%20CBI%2C%20and%20income%20tax%20intensified%20raids%20on%20its%20leaders%2C%20including%20candidates.%20They%20were%20harassed%20and%20put%20under%20strain%20while%20not%20a%20single%20BJP%20leader%20was%20subjected%20to%20similar%20treatment.%20The%20ED%2FCBI%2FIT%20cannot%20demoralise%20Congress%20workers%2C%20says%20Kharge.%20But%20they%20did%20frustrate%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20work%2C%20and%20it%20did%20disrupt%20their%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20these%20assembly%20elections%20heralded%20another%2C%20far%20more%20alarming%20trend.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20party%20has%20field-tested%20a%20cloak-and-dagger%20%E2%80%98influence%E2%80%99%20operation%20aimed%20at%20sabotaging%20the%20political%20fortunes%20of%20its%20rivals.%C2%A0The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F41fda598-c7f9-4427-a398-492fcc2aa844%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%3ELokniti%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20referred%20to%20a%20sudden%20swing%20in%20voters%E2%80%99%20mood%20some%20time%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20November.%20Development%20issues%2C%20which%20were%20the%20dominant%20theme%20earlier%2C%20took%20a%20back%20seat%20after%20November%203%20(four%20days%20before%20the%20polling%20on%20November%207)%20when%20the%20ED%20came%20out%20with%20its%20allegation%20of%20a%20Rs%20508%20crore%20%E2%80%98Mahadev%20scam%E2%80%99%20against%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20should%20draw%20the%20right%20lessons%20from%20this%20episode.%20This%20must%20be%20viewed%20as%20a%20rehearsal%20for%20more%20daring%20influence%20operations%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsider%20the%20present%20regime%E2%80%99s%20proclivity%20to%20undertake%20audacious%20operations%20even%20in%20foreign%20lands.%C2%A0This%20has%20led%20to%C2%A0much%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fdde7635b-dfbd-41ea-97ec-fd10bf477294%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%3Ediplomatic%20tension%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20friendly%20countries.%20This%20adds%20to%20the%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20fears%20of%20a%20last-minute%20Modi%20gambit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20the%20Electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20virtually%20legalises%20unaccounted%20money%20and%20puts%20it%20into%20the%20kitty%20of%20the%20preferred%20political%20party.%20The%20sale%20of%20the%20latest%20tranche%20of%20bonds%20happened%20in%20November%2C%20just%20in%20time%20for%20the%20five%20state%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F2580859c-d683-4592-89bd-5b4526bad27c%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F2580859c-d683-4592-89bd-5b4526bad27c%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1702536247409000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0K7Bn0crZrYwuQQtEZFCI8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAs%20per%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reform%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20BJP%20was%20the%20biggest%20beneficiary%20of%20the%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Scheme.%20It%20bagged%20Rs%205%2C272%20core%20out%20of%20a%20total%20Rs%209%2C188%20crore.%20Other%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20regional%20parties%2C%20shared%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20further%20skews%20the%20political%20environment%20for%20the%20political%20opposition%20by%20legalising%20a%20black%2C%20opaque%20means%20of%20money%20reaching%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20on%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20bonds%20scheme%20is%20expected%20any%20day.%C2%A0A%20lot%20hangs%20on%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EP.%20Raman%20is%20a%20veteran%20journalist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702454450000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F12114331%2F33F81A3F-BCF6-4D05-975C-264958F029F4_1_105_c.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-triumph-of-the-modi-model-rests-on-three-key-weapons%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP's%20victory%20in%20the%20Hindu%20heartland%20states%20has%20once%20again%20demonstrated%20the%20devious%20means%20the%20party%20uses%20to%20skew%20the%20political%20environment%20for%20the%20opposition%20by%20misusing%20probe%20agencies%20and%20gaining%20undue%20benefit%20from%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-triumph-of-the-modi-model-rests-on-three-key-weapons%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stubble-Burning%20Incidents%20Down%20by%2054.2%25%20in%20the%20Latest%20Paddy%20Harvesting%20Season%3A%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F14145605%2F6314806215_7aa3972351_b.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EStubble-burning%20incidents%20in%20states%20with%20major%20paddy%20cultivation%20have%20reduced%20by%2054.2%25%20during%20the%20recent%2045-day%20paddy%20harvesting%20season%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20told%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaddy%20stubble%20burning%20is%20the%20practice%20of%20burning%20leftover%20plant%20debris%20after%20harvesting%20rice%20to%20prepare%20fields%20for%20wheat%20crops.%20The%20Union%20government%20data%20estimates%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fsci-tech%2Fenergy-and-environment%2Fdelhi-pollution-woes-majorly-due-to-stubble-burning-centre%2Farticle67518519.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCentral%2520government%2520sources%2520said%252038%2Cwas%2520contributed%2520by%2520stubble%2520burning.%5C%22%3E38%25%20of%20the%20air%20pollution%20level%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20contributed%20by%20stubble%20burning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20data%20presented%20by%20Union%20agriculture%20and%20farmers%E2%80%99%20welfare%20minister%2C%20Arjun%20Munda%2C%20to%20the%20parliament%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20December%2012%2C%20the%20number%20of%20incidents%20reduced%20from%2013%2C964%20(in%202022)%20to%206%2C391%20(in%202023)%20during%20the%20September%2015%20to%20October%2029%20period%20across%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20NCR-Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20NCR-Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Delhi.%20In%202021%2C%20these%20regions%20together%20accounted%20for%2011%2C461%20stubble-burning%20incidents%20in%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20and%20Haryana%20had%20registered%2012%2C112%20and%201%2C813%20incidents%2C%20respectively%2C%20in%202022.%20The%20corresponding%20figures%20for%20this%20year%20came%20down%20to%205%2C254%20and%201%2C094%20in%20the%20September%2015%20to%20October%2029%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agriculture%20minister%20told%20the%20House%20that%20a%20satellite%20remote%20sensing%20system%20is%20in%20place%20to%20track%20active%20fires.%20The%20system%20was%20developed%20by%20the%20Consortium%20for%20Research%20on%20Agroecosystem%20Monitoring%20and%20Modelling%20from%20Space%20Laboratory%2C%20Division%20of%20Agricultural%20Physics%2C%20ICAR-Indian%20Agricultural%20Research%20Institute%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2010%2C%202021%2C%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%2C%20through%20statutory%20directions%2C%20came%20out%20with%20a%20framework%20for%20control%2Felimination%20of%20crop%20residue%20burning%2C%20mandating%20governments%20of%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20develop%20state-specific%20actionable%20plans.%20The%20plans%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20include%20proper%20implementation%20of%20in-situ%20and%20ex-situ%20management%20of%20paddy%20straw%2C%20effective%20monitoring%2Fenforcement%2C%20and%20the%20prohibition%20of%20stubble%20burning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20overall%20air%20quality%20in%20Delhi%20stood%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98very%20poor%E2%80%99%20category%20with%20the%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20standing%20at%20326%2C%20as%20per%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(CPCB)%20data%20registered%20at%207%20am%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20December%2012%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Fdelhi-no-longer-indias-most-polluted-city-bihar-uttar-pradesh-sees-worst-aqi-check-full-list-here-11702342673449.html%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveMint%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20An%20AQI%20between%20zero%20and%2050%20is%20considered%20%E2%80%98good%E2%80%99%2C%2051%20and%20100%20%E2%80%98satisfactory%E2%80%99%2C%20101%20and%20200%20%E2%80%98moderate%E2%80%99%2C%20201%20and%20300%20%E2%80%98poor%E2%80%99%2C%20301%20and%20400%20%E2%80%98very%20poor%E2%80%99%2C%20401%20and%20450%20%E2%80%98severe%E2%80%99%20and%20above%20450%20%E2%80%98severe-plus%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702452601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F14145605%2F6314806215_7aa3972351_b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fstubble-burning-incidents-down-by-54-2-in-the-latest-paddy-harvesting-season-centre%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20number%20of%20incidents%20reduced%20from%2013%2C964%20(in%202022)%20to%206%2C391%20(in%202023)%20during%20the%20September%2015%20to%20October%2029%20period%20across%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20NCR-Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20