7-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20has%20asked%20his%20counterpart%20in%20neighbouring%20Mizoram%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20what%20he%20has%20described%20as%20his%20state%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cinternal%20matters%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20comes%20just%20days%20after%20a%20new%20chief%20minister%20was%20sworn%20in%20in%20Mizoram%20but%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Singh%20has%20opened%20hostilities%20with%20a%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20amidst%20raging%20ethnic%20strife%20between%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20the%20Kukis%20in%20Manipur%2C%20Singh%20had%20criticised%20the%20then%20Mizoram%20chief%20minister%20Zoramthanga%20for%20meddling%20with%20his%20state%E2%80%99s%20affairs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20least%2012%2C000%20Kukis%20had%20fled%20to%20Mizoram%20during%20the%20strife%20that%20began%20this%20May%2C%20and%20several%20have%20since%20been%20staying%20there%2C%20as%20the%20violence%20has%20not%20completely%20stopped.%20The%20Kukis%20are%2C%20as%20a%20tribe%2C%20kindred%20to%20the%20Mizos%2C%20the%20largest%20community%20of%20that%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20news%20reports%2C%20the%20war%20of%20words%20began%20after%20new%20Mizoram%20chief%20minister%20Lalduhoma%20asked%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20not%20to%20harass%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20people%20residing%20in%20the%20border%20town%20of%20Moreh.%20Lalduhoma%20had%20made%20those%20comments%20in%20his%20interactions%20with%20local%20media%20after%20taking%20over%20the%20reins%20of%20the%20state.%20He%20had%20said%20that%20Kukis%20were%20not%20being%20treated%20well%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoreh%2C%20located%20about%20four%20kilometres%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20border%20with%20Myanmar%2C%20is%20home%20to%20not%20only%20Kukis%20but%20also%20to%20a%20sizeable%20population%20of%20Tamils%20displaced%20from%20Myanmar%20(then%20Burma)%20during%20the%20World%20War%20II%2C%20besides%20Meitei%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20(Pangals)%20and%20some%20other%20tribes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fembed%3Fpb%3D!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d14551.241314661123!2d94.29111590345352!3d24.24841175333876!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x37497a16054fb52f%253A0xab12dc86609ab0c6!2sMoreh%252C%2520Manipur!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1702447498538!5m2!1sen!2sin%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20in%20Imphal%20on%20December%2012%2C%20Singh%20retorted%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhatever%20happened%20in%20Manipur%20is%20our%20internal%20matter.%20But%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20I%20have%20seen%20comments%20from%20the%20newly%20elected%20chief%20minister%20of%20Mizoram%20that%20state%20police%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20harass%20his%20people%20in%20Moreh.%20It%20is%20beyond%20the%20constitution%20to%20talk%20about%20Manipur%20as%20it%20is%20our%20internal%20matter.%20He%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20Moreh.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMedia%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fbiren-tells-mizoram-cm-lalduhoma-to-keep-off-manipur-affairs%2Farticleshow%2F105941913.cms%5C%22%3Ereports%20also%20quoted%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20communities%20reside%20in%20Moreh%20%E2%80%93%20Meiteis%2C%20Tamils%2C%20Kukis%2C%20Meitei-Pangal%2C%20Thadaou%20%E2%80%93%20all%20are%20living%20there.%20So%20it%20cannot%20be%20taken%20as%20a%20one%20community%20area.%20My%20earnest%20appeal%20to%20him%20is%2C%20pelase%20help%20us%20restore%20peace.%20I%20never%20commented%20when%20the%20Bru%20issues%20(the%20ethnic%20strife%20between%20Br