5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20nine%20other%20small-scale%20farmers%2C%20Sanjay%20harvested%208%2C000%20pearls%20in%20an%20acre%20of%20pond%2C%20earning%20them%20Rs%2040%20lakh.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20him%20to%20understand%20the%20nitty-gritty%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F229545%2Fagra-woman-entrepreneur-grow-oysters-pearl-farming-home-earn-lakhs-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoyster%20pearl%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20group%20of%20farmers%20was%20able%20to%20earn%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20by%20selling%208%2C000%20pearls.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334696%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20group%20of%20farmers%20was%20able%20to%20earn%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20by%20selling%208%2C000%20pearls.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHarvesting%20pearls%20in%20water-scarce%20land%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20pursuing%20a%20Diploma%20in%20Medical%20Laboratory%20Technology%20(DMLT)%2C%20Sanjay%20works%20part-time%20as%20a%20